fore%20he%20is%20set%20to%20formally%20retire.%20Balamurugan%20had%20been%20in%20the%20news%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20for%20criticising%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20and%20demanding%20her%20sacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalamurugan%20had%C2%A0%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Firs-officer-seeks-dismissal-of-fm-nirmala-over-ed-summons-to-tn-farmers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewritten%20to%20President%20Murumu%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3Eaccusing%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20of%20becoming%20an%20extended%20arm%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20The%20officer%E2%80%99s%20letter%20came%20after%20the%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Ftwo-elderly-dalit-farmers-fighting-case-against-tn-bjp-leader-summoned-by-ed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EED%20sent%20a%20summons%20to%20two%20Dalit%20farmers%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3Ein%20Tamil%20Nadu%20who%20were%20locked%20in%20a%20legal%20tussle%20with%20a%20local%20BJP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalamurugan%2C%20who%20was%20holding%20the%20post%20of%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Goods%20and%20Service%20Tax%20(GST)%20in%20Chennai%2C%20had%20said%20that%20Sitharaman%20had%20successfully%20converted%20the%20ED%20into%20a%20BJP%20policy%20enforcement%20directorate.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20he%20had%20demanded%20the%20dismissal%20of%20the%20Union%20finance%20minister%2C%20whom%20he%20called%20%E2%80%9Cunfit%20to%20be%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%202024%20Elections%20Near%2C%20ED%20Accelerates%20Actions%20Against%20Opposition%20Leaders%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-2024-elections-near-ed-accelerates-actions-against-opposition-leaders%5C%22%3EAs%202024%20Elections%20Near%2C%20ED%20Accelerates%20Actions%20Against%20Opposition%20Leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%20two%20Dalit%20farmers%2C%20Kannaiyan%20and%20Krishnan%2C%20both%20in%20their%2070s%20and%20living%20in%20Attur%20of%20Salem%20district%2C%20received%20summons%20from%20the%20ED.%20While%20it%20remains%20unclear%20as%20to%20why%20the%20ED%20summoned%20the%20brothers%2C%20who%20own%206.5%20acres%20of%20agricultural%20land%20in%20their%20village%2C%20the%20reference%20to%20them%20as%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Pallars%E2%80%99%20triggered%20outrage.%20It%20was%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20ED%20is%20targeting%20the%20farmers%20%E2%80%93%20who%20subsist%20on%20a%20Rs%201%2C000%20monthly%20pension%20%E2%80%93%20since%20they%20are%20engaged%20in%20a%20land%20dispute%20case%20against%20Gunashekar%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Salem%20East%20district%20secretary%2C%20whom%20the%20farmers%20have%20accused%20of%20illegally%20trying%20to%20grab%20their%20land.%20The%20ED%20had%20said%20on%20January%204%2C%20that%20they%C2%A0%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fed-to-close-case-against-2-dalit-farmers-in-tamil-nadu-following-backlash%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewould%20close%20the%20case%20against%20the%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%2C%20which%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20do.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20Balamurgan%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Dalit%20Pravina%20is%20the%20lawyer%20representing%20the%20two%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20president%20regarding%20this%20matter%2C%20Balmurugan%20had%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20shows%20how%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20become%20an%20extended%20arm%20of%20the%20BJP.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitaraman%2C%20after%20taking%20over%20the%20charge%2C%20has%20successfully%20converted%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20into%20BJP%20Policy%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fnews%2Fi-find-strength-in-his-legacy-rohith-vemulas-mother-on-his-birthday%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20News%20Minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706675187000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31095524%2Fbb-irs.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftamil-nadu-irs-officer-who-complained-to-president-against-nirmala-sitharaman-transferred%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22B.%20Balamurugan%20had%20accused%20the%20Union%20finance%20minister%20of%20turning%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20into%20an%20arm%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftamil-nadu-irs-officer-who-complained-to-president-against-nirmala-sitharaman-transferred%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Under%20Virat's%20captaincy%2C%20India%20wouldn't%20have%20lost%20to%20England'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706674943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107279004%2Cimgsize-57134.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fengland-in-india%2Funder-virat-kohlis-captaincy-india-wouldnt-have-lost-1st-test-against-england-rohit-sharma-switched-off-michael-vaughan%2Farticleshow%2F107278892.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20spite%20of%20securing%20a%20big%20first-innings%20lead%2C%20India%20faced%20defeat%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20England.%20This%20outcome%20is%20seldom%20experienced%20by%20India%2C%20especially%20in%20spin-friendly%20home