ceived%20notices%20from%20the%20ED%20before%20and%20termed%20those%20part%20of%20political%20vendetta%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%2C%20wrote%20to%20the%20ED%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20will%20record%20his%20statement%20with%20the%20agency%20on%20January%2031%20at%20his%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoren%20is%20the%20fourth%20opposition%20chief%20minister%20to%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20central%20investigation%20agency.%20Earlier%2C%20former%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20his%20associates%20were%20accused%20by%20the%20ED%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20an%20illegal%20online%20betting%20case.%20Baghel%20was%20named%20by%20the%20ED%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20assembly%20polls%2C%20which%20allowed%20the%20BJP%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20political%20campaign%20against%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20corruption.%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20and%20his%20son%20and%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20have%20also%20been%20implicated%20in%20an%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cland%20for%20jobs%E2%80%9D%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20chief%20minister%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20served%20multiple%20notices%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20the%20excise%20policy%20case%2C%20in%20which%20his%20deputy%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20party%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20have%20already%20been%20arrested.%20Satyendra%20Jain%2C%20another%20AAP%20minister%20in%20Delhi%2C%20has%20been%20in%20prison%20for%20around%20two%20years.%20Speculations%20are%20rife%20that%20Kejriwal%20may%20soon%20be%20arrested%20for%20refusing%20to%20present%20himself%20for%20questioning%2C%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20questioning%20was%20politically%20motivated%20and%20a%20ploy%20to%20arrest%20him%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20campaigning%20during%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22BJP%20Wins%20Chandigarh%20Mayoral%20Polls%20Amid%20Rigging%20Allegations%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-wins-chandigarh-mayoral-polls-amid-rigging-allegations%5C%22%3EBJP%20Wins%20Chandigarh%20Mayoral%20Polls%20Amid%20Rigging%20Allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20one%20has%20seen%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20BJP%20used%20the%20raid%20against%20Soren%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fhemant-soren-delhi-house-ed-seize-cash-bmw-9134607%2F%5C%22%3Elaunch%20a%20shrill%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister.%20Immediately%20after%20the%20raids%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20when%20Soren%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20present%2C%20the%20BJP%20put%20up%20a%20%E2%80%98missing%20person%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20poster%20containing%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20picture%20and%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2011%2C000%20for%20the%20person%20who%20finds%20him%2C%20and%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20gone%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20what%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20claim%20that%20Soren%20had%20been%20absconding.%20However%2C%20Soren%20emerged%20in%20the%20afternoon%20and%20attended%20a%20meeting%20with%20his%20party%20legislators.%20Soren%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20been%20preoccupied%20with%20prior%20scheduled%20official%20engagements%20and%20preparations%20for%20the%20state%20budget%2C%20and%20accused%20the%20ED%20of%20conducting%20raids%20out%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmalice%E2%80%9D%20and%20to%20further%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20agenda%E2%80%9D%20of%20disrupting%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20even%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20who%20is%20severely%20ill%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fland-for-job-scam-case-rjd-chief-lalu-prasad-yadav-appears-before-ed-for-questioning%2Farticle67788200.ece%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20questioning%20by%20the%20ED%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20case%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20had%20first%20registered%20in%20May%202022%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cland-for-jobs%E2%80%9D%20scam.%20The%20CBI%20has%20named%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Rabri%20Devi%2C%20and%20their%20son%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20two%20daughters%20Misa%20Bharti%20and%20Hema%20Yadav%2C%20along%20with%2012%20others.%20The%20charges%20pertain%20to%20taking%20alleged%20land%20bribes%20in%20exchange%20for%20Group%20D%20jobs%20given%20by%20the%20Union%20railway%20ministry%20when%20Lalu%20was%20the%20railway%20minister%2C%20between%202004%20to%202009.%20Incidentally%2C%20Prasad%E2%80%99s%20son%20Tejashwi%20was%20a%20teenager%20back%20then.%20One%20of%20Prasad%E2%80%99s%20daughters%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Misa%20Bharti%2C%20accompanied%20her%20father%20to%20the%20ED%20office%2C%20and%20said%20that%20her%20family%20was%20being%20%E2%80%9Cunnecessarily%20harassed%E2%80%9D%20although%20it%20has%20categorically%20said%20that%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20cooperate%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20his%20father%20was%20questioned%2C%20Tejashwi%20was%20called%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20questioned%20for%20over%20eight%20hours%20in%20the%20same%20case%2C%20amidst%20calls%20by%20opposition%20leaders%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmisusing%E2%80%9D%20the%20agencies%20for%20its%20own%20political%20gains.%20After%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20his%20supporters%20rallied%20behind%20him%2C%20in%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20show%20of%20strength.%20Responding%20to%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20questioning%20at%20the%20ED%20office%2C%20party%20MP%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Jha%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20agency%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20ED%20office%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20office%20where%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20has%20come.%20When%20elections%20come%2C%20opposition%20parties%E2%80%99%20leaders%20are%20summoned%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20when%20the%20supporters%20of%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%2C%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bengals-sandeshkhali-controversial-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahans-hold-is-powerful%5C%22%3Eattacked%20ED%20officials%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20they%20had%20come%20to%20search%20the%20leader%E2%80%99s%20premises%20in%20connection%20with%20one%20alleged%20Public%20Distribution%20Scheme%20scam%2C%20the%20BJP%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20communal%20issue%20by%20demonising%20the%20Muslim%20community%20and%20accusing%20the%20TMC%20for%20%E2%80%9Cappeasing%E2%80%9D%20the%20minority%20community.%20However%2C%20on%20January%2024%2C%20the%20ED%20officials%20successfully%20carried%20out%20a%20raid%20at%20his%20house%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district.%20Another%20TMC%20minister%2C%20Jyoti%20Priya%20Mallick%2C%20has%20already%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20central%20agency%20in%20October%202023%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20same%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20central%20agencies%2C%20the%20latest%20being%20former%20Congress%20minister%20in%20Rajasthan%20Mahesh%20Joshi%20in%20the%20alleged%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20scam%2C%20associates%20of%20a%20few%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20in%20an%20alleged%20Haryana%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20scam%2C%20and%20several%20local%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20southern%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Pre-Election%20Swoop%20Is%20the%20Central%20Agencies%E2%80%99%20Latest%20Trick%20Against%20Opposition%20Leaders%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpre-election-swoop-central-agencies-latest-trick-opposition-leaders%5C%22%3EThe%20Pre-Election%20Swoop%20Is%20the%20Central%20Agencies%E2%80%99%20Latest%20Trick%20Against%20O