status%2F1752334475873403324%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2030%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20national%20wrestling%20championship%20organised%20by%20the%20Sports%20Ministry%20is%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20but%20Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20illegally%20organising%20a%20separate%20national%20championship%20to%20assert%20his%20dominance%20and%20signing%20certificates%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Malikkh%20alleged%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20sportspersons%20seek%20jobs%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20these%20certificates%2C%20they%20will%20face%20action%20even%20though%20they%20are%20not%20at%20fault.%20Action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WFI%20panel%20was%20suspended%20last%20month%2C%20days%20after%20it%20was%20elected%2C%20over%20hasty%20announcement%20of%20Under-15%20and%20Under-20%20nationals.%20Suspending%20the%20body%2C%20the%20ministry%20also%20said%20the%20new%20body%20was%20working%20under%20complete%20control%20of%20former%20office-bearers%20-%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20BJP%20MP%20and%20former%20WFI%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20the%20former%20wrestling%20boss%20had%20sparked%20a%20protest%20by%20the%20country's%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20Ms%20Malikkh%2C%20Bajrang%20Punia%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat.%20After%20several%20delays%20due%20to%20court%20battles%2C%20an%20election%20to%20form%20a%20new%20panel%20was%20held%20in%20December%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20an%20aide%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20was%20elected%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisappointed%20at%20the%20results%2C%20Ms%20Malikkh%20announced%20a%20shocking%20decision%20to%20quit%20wrestling%20and%20put%20her%20boots%20on%20the%20table%20during%20a%20media%20interaction.%20Days%20later%2C%20Mr%20Punia%20returned%20his%20Padma%20Shri%20in%20protes