22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107277805%2Cimgsize-1817812.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fexplorers-may-have-found-wreckage-of-amelia-earharts-plane-in-pacific%2Farticleshow%2F107277619.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107277619.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EEarhart%2C%20an%20iconic%20figure%20in%20aviation%20history%2C%20vanished%20in%201937%20with%20navigator%20Fred%20Noonan%20while%20attempting%20a%20historic%20flight%20around%20the%20world.%20If%20successful%2C%20Earhart%20would%20have%20been%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat.%20Deep%20Sea%20Vision's%20discovery%2C%20made%20using%20sonar%20data%20from%20a%20deep-sea%20drone%2C%20could%20end%20an%2087-year-old%20mystery.%20The%20sonar%20images%2C%20though%20blurry%2C%20depict%20contours%20that%20strikingly%20resemble%20Earhart's%20Lockheed%20Model%2010-E%20Electra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fexplorers-may-have-found-wreckage-of-amelia-earharts-plane-in-pacific%2Farticleshow%2F107277619.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fexplorers-may-have-found-wreckage-of-amelia-earharts-plane-in-pacific%2Famp_articleshow%2F107277619.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fexplorers-may-have-found-wreckage-of-amelia-earharts-plane-in-pacific%2Famp_articleshow%2F107277619.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Murder%20In%20Gujarat%2C%20Drugs%20In%20Australia%3A%20Indian-Origin%20Couple's%20Empire%20Falls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20story%20chillingly%20similar%20to%20the%20acclaimed%20TV%20series%20Ozark%2C%20an%20Indian-origin%20couple%20living%20in%20the%20UK%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%2033%20years%20in%20prison%20each%20for%20a%20crime%20that%20transcends%20international%20borders.%20Arti%20Dhir%2C%2059%2C%20and%20Kavaljitsinh%20Raijada%2C%2035%2C%20from%20West%20London's%20Ealing%2C%20are%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20multi-million-pound%20drug%20trafficking%20operation%20that%20spanned%20continents%2C%20mirroring%20the%20intricate%20webs%20of%20deceit%20portrayed%20in%20the%20popular%20crime%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Crime%20Agency%20(NCA)%20unraveled%20the%20elaborate%20scheme%20when%20the%20Australian%20Border%20Force%20intercepted%20over%20half%20a%20tonne%20of%20cocaine%2C%20valued%20at%20a%20staggering%2057%20million%20pounds%2C%20which%20is%20over%20Rs%20600%20crore%2C%20upon%20its%20arrival%20in%20Sydney%20in%20May%202021.%20The%20drug-laden%20cargo%2C%20cleverly%20concealed%20within%20metal%20toolboxes%2C%20was%20traced%20back%20to%20the%20seemingly%20ordinary%20couple%20who%20had%20established%20a%20front%20company%20named%20Viefly%20Freight%20Services%20to%20facilitate%20their%20drugs%20smuggling%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Cocaine%20Caper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20court%20heard%20that%20the%20couple's%20front%20company%20had%20dispatched%20the%20narcotics%20via%20a%20commercial%20flight%20from%20the%20UK.%20When%20authorities%20cracked%20open%20the%20metal%20toolboxes%2C%20they%20discovered%20a%20staggering%20514%20kilograms%20of%20cocaine.%20The%20street%20value%20of%20this%20illicit%20cargo%20in%20Australia%2C%20where%20drug%20prices%20soar%20well%20above%20those%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20was%20estimated%20to%20be%2057%20million%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhir%20and%20Raijada%20vehemently%20denied%20the%20charges%20of%20exporting%20cocaine%20to%20Australia%20and%20money%20laundering.%20However%2C%20a%20jury%20at%20Southwark%20Crown%20Court%20convicted%20them%20on%2012%20counts%20of%20exportation%20and%2018%20counts%20of%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeb%20Of%20Deceit%20Unraveled%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCA%20connected%20the%20dots%20leading%20to%20the%20convicted%20couple.%20Raijada's%20fingerprints%20on%20the%20plastic%20wrappings%20of%20the%20toolboxes%20and%20receipts%20found%20at%20their%20residence%20were%20key%20evidence%20linking%20them%20to%20the%20crime.%20The%20agency%20revealed%20that%20the%20couple%20had%20orchestrated%2037%20consignments%20to%20Australia%20since%20June%202019%2C%20with%2022%20acting%20as%20decoys%20and%2015%20containing%20cocaine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Dhir%20and%20Raijada%20had%20prior%20employment%20at%20a%20Heathrow%20flight%20services%20company%2C%20exploiting%20their%20insider%20knowledge%20of%20airport%20freight%20procedures%20to%20cloak%20their%20illicit%20activities.%20The%20intricate%20scheme%2C%20however%2C%20began%20to%20unravel%20when%20the%20couple%20was%20arrested%20at%20their%20Hanwell%20residence%20on%20June%2021%2C%202021%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20discovery%20of%20substantial%20amounts%20of%20cash%20and%20gold-plated%20silver%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoney%20Trail%20And%20A%20Failsafe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20in%20February%20last%20year%20exposed%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20couple's%20hidden%20wealth.%C2%A0NCA%20officers%20uncovered%20almost%203%20million%20pounds%20in%20cash%20concealed%20in%20boxes%20and%20suitcases%20at%20a%20storage%20unit%20in%20West%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinancial%20inquiries%20revealed%20that%20despite%20declaring%20meager%20profits%2C%20the%20couple%20had%20purchased%20a%20flat%20in%20Ealing%20for%20800%2C000%20pounds%20(approx.%20Rs%208.5%20crore)%20and%20a%20Land%20Rover%20for%2062%2C000%20pounds.%20Their%20cash%20deposits%20of%20nearly%20740%2C000%20pounds%20into%2022%20different%20bank%20accounts%20since%202019%20raised%20suspicions%20of%20extensive%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArti%20Dhir%20and%20Kavaljitsinh%20Raijada%20used%20their%20insider%20knowledge%20of%20the%20air%20freight%20industry%20to%20traffic%20cocaine%20worth%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20pounds%20from%20the%20UK%20to%20Australia%2C%20where%20they%20knew%20they%20could%20maximise%20their%20revenue%2C%26quot%3B%20Piers%20Phillips%2C%20NCA%20Senior%20Investigating%20Officer%2C%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMurder%20Allegations%20And%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20faced%20extradition%20sought%20by%20India%20on%20charges%20of%20murdering%20their%20adopted%20son%2C%20Gopal%20Sejani%2C%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%2011-year-old's%20tragic%20fate%20unfolded%20in%20February%202017%2C%20with%20Indian%20police%20alleging%20a%20sinister%20plot%20involving%20adoption%2C%20insurance%2C%20and%20a%20staged%20kidnapping%20for%20an%20insurance%20payout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20who%20traveled%20to%20Gujarat%20in%202015%20to%20adopt%20Gopal%2C%20promised%20the%20young%20boy%20a%20better%20life%20in%20London.%20However%2C%20Gopal%20was%20abducted%2C%20stabbed%2C%20and%20left%20by%20a%20roadside%20on%20February%208%2C%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20reportedly%20placed%20an%20advertisement%20in%20a%20local%20newspaper%2C%20enticing%20prospective%20parents%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20bringing%20an%20adopted%20child%20to%20live%20in%20London.%20Gopal%2C%20a%20farm%20boy%20living%20with%20his%20older%20sister%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20became%20the%20target%20of%20their%20plan.%20Indian%20police%20alleged%20that%20Dhir%20and%20Raijada%20had%20ulterior%20motives%20beyond%20providing%20a%20home%20for%20Gopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20extradition%20request%20was%20denied%20in%202019%2C%20followed%20by%20an%20unsuccessful%20appeal%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20in%20London%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706671200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fuuqvpsf4_indian-couple-jailed-in-uk_625x300_31_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fmurder-in-gujarat-drugs-in-australia-indian-origin-couples-empire-falls-4964422%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20chilling%20tale%20that%20seems%20plucked%20from%20the%20script%20of%20the%20acclaimed%20TV%20series%20Ozark%2C%20an%20Indian-origin%20couple%20residing%20in%20the%20UK%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%2033%20years%20in%20prison%20each%20for%20a%20crime%20that%20transcends%20international%20borders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fmurder-in-gujarat-drugs-in-australia-indian-origin-couples-empire-falls-4964422%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fmurder-in-gujarat-drugs-in-australia-indian-origin-couples-empire-falls-4964422%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fmurder-in-gujarat-drugs-in-australia-indian-origin-couples-empire-falls-4964422%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Changes%20Will%20Rohit%20Make%20To%20Replace%20Injured%20Jadeja%2C%20Rahul%20In%202nd%20Test%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUntimely%20injuries%20to%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20K%20L%20Rahul%20have%20given%20a%20major%20selection%20headache%20to%20India%20as%20they%20seek%20to%20bounce%20back%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20against%20England%2C%20following%20a%20rare%20defeat%20at%20home.%20Both%20Jadeja%20and%20Rahul%20were%20among%20India's%20main%20performers%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20of%20the%20Hyderabad%20Test%20before%20England%20turned%20the%20tables%20on%20the%20formidable%20hosts.%20Jadeja%20sustained%20a%20hamstring%20injury%20while%20going%20for%20a%20quick%20single%20during%20the%20Hyderabad%20Test%20while%20Rahul%20has%20complained%20of%20pain%20in%20his%20right%20quadriceps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo's%20unavailability%20adds%20to%20the%20woes%20of%20the%20home%20side%2C%20which%20was%20clearly%20stunned%20by%20England's%20'Bazball'%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadeja%2C%20with%20his%20exceptional%20all-round%20abilities%2C%20makes%20himself%20almost%20irreplaceable%20and%20Rahul%20too%20has%20been%20among%20India's%20standout%20batters%20across%20the%20ODI%20and%20Test%20format%20since%20returning%20from%20a%20surgery%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20remains%20unavailable%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons%20and%20after%20a%20shock%20reverse%20in%20the%20series%20opener%2C%20the%20management%20will%20be%20missing%20him%20even%20more%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20where%20the%20second%20Test%20begins%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20and%20Rahul%20Dravid%20have%20enough%20options%20to%20choose%20from%20with%20selectors%20adding%20three%20players%20to%20the%20squad%20--%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%2C%20Sourabh%20Kumar%20and%20Washington%20Sundar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20straightforward%20selection%20will%20be%20Rajat%20Patidar%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%2015%20in%20Hyderabad.%20He%20could%20take%20Rahul's%20place%20in%20the%20middle-order%20with%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20replacing%20Jadeja%20as%20the%20third%20spinner%20alongside%20R%20Ashwin%20and%20Axar%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20option%20for%20India%20is%20to%20do%20what%20England%20did%20in%20the%20opener%2C%20play%20only%20one%20pacer%20for%20four%20spin%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20case%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20could%20make%20way%20for%20Kuldeep%20and%20the%20team%20can%20accommodate%20either%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20or%20Washington%20to%20solidify%20the%20middle-order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESourabh%2C%20who%20also%20bowls%20left-arm%20spin%20like%20Jadeja%20and%20is%20a%20decent%20batter%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20first-class%20hundreds%20to%20his%20name%2C%20can%20be%20a%20dark%20horse%20in%20that%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACA-VDCA%20Stadium%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20has%20staged%20two%20Tests%20till%20date%20and%20the%20pitch%20is%20usually%20a%20batting%20friendly%20one%20at%20least%20in%20the%20first%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBatting%20first%20at%20the%20venue%20back%20in%202019%2C%20India%20had%20racked%20up%20502%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20against%20South%20Africa%20with%20Mayank%20Agarwal%20getting%20a%20double%20hundred%20and%20Rohit%20scoring%20a%20brisk%20176%20in%20his%20first%20innings%20as%20a%20Test%20opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpin%20legend%20Anil%20Kumble%20feels%20wrist%20spinner%20Kuldeep's%20presence%20in%20the%20eleven%20will%20be%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20India%20feel%20that%20they%20need%20only%20one%20fast%20bowler%20then%20having%20Kuldeep%20will%20certainly%20help.%20He%20will%20have%20variations%20but%20England%20will%20come%20and%20do%20the%20same%20things%20they%20did%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumble%20told%20the%20host%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20wicket%20could%20be%20a%20turning%20one%20and%20we%20are%20expecting%20the%20pace%20to%20be%20quicker%20than%20this.%20This%20was%20slow%20but%20it%20was%20a%20good%20wicket%20if%20you%20applied%20yourself.%20India%20certainly%20need%20to%20buckle%20up%20with%20their%20approach%20to%20playing%20against%20spin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20felt%20that%20they%20were%20certainly%20rattled%20by%20the%20way%20England%20approached%20their%20batting%20and%20with%20that%2C%20they%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20plans%2C%20some%20unconventional%20ones.%20They%20never%20tried%20any%20variations%20so%20that's%20something%20I%20am%20sure%20they%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20referring%20to%20the%20spin%20trio%20being%20put%20under%20pressure%20with%20England's%20relentless%20sweeping%20tactic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20showed%20plenty%20of%20promise%20in%20his%20four-Test%20career%2C%20left-handed%20batter%20Washington%20who%20bowls%20right%20hand%20off-spin%2C%20also%20makes%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20making%20his%20debut%20in%20the%20iconic%20Test%20win%20at%20the%20Gabba%2C%20he%20featured%20in%20three%20games%20in%20the%20previous%20home%20series%20against%20England%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20managed%20an%2085%20not%20out%20and%2096%20not%20out%20in%20five%20innings%20over%20the%20course%20of%20that%20series%20and%20picked%20up%20two%20wickets%20in%20a%20rubber%20dominated%20by%20front-line%20spinners%20Ashwin%20and%20Axar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20selector%20Sarandeep%20Singh%2C%20during%20whose%20tenure%20Washington%20made%20his%20debut%20Down%20Under%2C%20said%20the%20all-rounder%20is%20a%20utility%20player%20but%20he%20would%20not%20want%20to%20tinker%20too%20much%20with%20the%20playing%20eleven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20pretty%20simple%20for%20me.%20Rajat%20Patidar%20comes%20in%20for%20Rahul%20and%20Kuldeep%20comes%20in%20for%20Jadeja.%20We%20don't%20need%20to%20copy%20England%20and%20play%20four%20spinners.%20Playing%20with%20two%20pacers%20and%20three%20spinners%20has%20been%20our%20strength%20at%20home.%20We%20need%20to%20stick%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20India%20spinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20reckons%20it%20would%20be%20better%20for%20the%20team's%20cause%20if%20Rohit%20drops%20himself%20to%20number%203%20and%20an%20under-fire%20Shubman%20Gill%20opens%20the%20innings%20alongside%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%2C%20who%20himself%20had%20expressed%20the%20desire%20to%20play%20at%20three%2C%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20replicate%20his%20white%20ball%20form%20in%20the%20traditional%20format%20after%20having%20taken%20veteran%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara's%20place%20in%20the%20top-order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGill%20is%20not%20a%20number%20three%20player.%20He%20should%20open.%20Rohit%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20players%20of%20spin%20and%20can%20drop%20down%20to%20accommodate%20Gill%20at%20the%