.%20Notably%2C%20Mr%20Zain%20is%20a%20Pakistan-born%20Japanese%20citizen%20who%20has%20lived%20in%20Japan%20for%20two%20decades%2C%20went%20to%20school%20there%2C%20and%20is%20fluent%20in%20Japanese.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20have%20been%20cooperating%20with%20(police)%20because%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20important%20for%20maintaining%20public%20safety%2C%20but%20when%20it%20happened%20not%20once%20but%20more%20than%2010%20times%2C%20I%20began%20to%20have%20doubts%20indeed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20plaintiff%20is%20Matthew%2C%20a%20man%20of%20Indian%20heritage%C2%A0who%20has%20lived%20in%20Japan%20for%20more%20than%2020%20years%20and%20holds%20permanent%20residency.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20stopped%20and%20questioned%20by%20police%20officers%20on%20the%20street%C2%A0and%20is%20afraid%20to%20go%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20never%20knew%20what%20social%20withdrawal%20was%20until%20recently.%20I%20feel%20like%20every%20time%20I%20finish%20work%2C%20I'm%20hiding%20in%20my%20house%2C''%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20plaintiff%20is%20an%20American-born%20man%20who%20has%20faced%20the%20same%20type%20of%20questioning%20from%20Japanese%20people.%20He%20said%20he%20hoped%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20the%20issue%20among%20the%20Japanese%20population%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EReuters.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20lose...%20I%20want%20people%20to%20understand%20that%20this%20is%20an%20everyday%20occurrence%2C%20an%20everyday%20thing%20and%20that%20we%20have%20to%20do%20something%20to%20prevent%20that%20for%20the%20future%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20such%20lawsuit%20in%20Japan%2C%20according%20to%20their%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20defines%20racial%20profiling%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20process%20by%20which%20law%20enforcement%20relies%20on%20generalisations%20based%20on%20one's%20race%2C%20skin%20colour%2C%20descent%20or%20national%20or%20ethnic%20origin%2C%20rather%20than%20objective%20evidence%20or%20individual%20behaviour%2C%20to%20subject%20people%20to%20stops%2C%20detailed%20searches%2C%20identity%20checks%2C%20and%20investigations%2C%20or%20for%20deciding%20that%20an%20individual%20was%20engaged%20in%20criminal%20activity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20rising%20immigration%2C%20foreign-born%20residents%20account%20for%20only%202.3%20per%20cent%20of%20Japan's%20population%2C%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20shares%20in%20the%20OECD.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706668500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F8mchibuo_foreigners-in-japan_625x300_31_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-pak-us-born-residents-sue-japan-government-over-alleged-racial-profiling-4964207%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20trio%20said%20they%20have%20suffered%20distress%20from%20repeated%20police%20questioning%20based%20on%20their%20appearance%20and%20ethnicity%2C%20which%20they%20say%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20constitution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-pak-us-born-residents-sue-japan-government-over-alleged-racial-profiling-4964207%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-pak-us-born-residents-sue-japan-government-over-alleged-racial-profiling-4964207%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-pak-us-born-residents-sue-japan-government-over-alleged-racial-profiling-4964207%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varun%2C%20Arjun%2C%20Diljit%20locked%20in%20for%20'No%20Entry%202'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706668200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107275688%2Cimgsize-70868.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimes