g!%20Stay%20in%20the%20race%20and%20keep%20your%20name%20out%20there!%20Your%20opportunity%20is%20coming.%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20us%20just%20know%20that%20it%20is.%20Thank%20you%2C%20Nikki%2C%20for%20putting%20a%20sane%2C%20smart%2C%20thoughtful%2C%20and%20dignified%20face%20and%20mind%20and%20heart%20into%20the%20race.%20Thank%20you%20for%20what%20you%20do%20for%20America%20and%20the%20world!%20God%20bless%20you!%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Martha%20R.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPLEASE%20DO%20NOT%20GIVE%20UP%20YOUR%20FIGHT!!%20In%20a%20world%20that's%20become%20crazy%20with%20strife%2C%20we%20need%20a%20level%20headed%20conservative%20leader%20to%20navigate%20us%20through%20the%20insanity!%20NO%20ONE%20is%20more%20capable%20than%20you%20are%20to%20right%20the%20ship%2C%20and%20heal%20this%20great%20nation!%20WE%20NEED%20you%20Nikki!%20This%20country%20NEEDS%20you!%20Our%20allies%2C%20and%20the%20beautiful%20people%20of%20this%20world%20need%20you!%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20you%20give%20up%2C%20and%20I%20guarantee%20you%20there%20are%20millions%20more%20out%20there%20who%20feel%20exactly%20as%20I%20do!%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Michael%20B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStaci%20J.%20H%20had%20a%20suggestion%20for%20Haley%20--%20'Don't%20quit!'%20%26quot%3BI%20encourage%20you%20to%20keep%20moving%20forward%20in%20your%20campaign.%20I%20am%20distressed%20that%20there%20may%20be%20another%20Trump%2FBiden%20race.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20neither%20of%20these%20men%20are%20people%20of%20integrity%2C%20and%20I%20am%20also%20concerned%20about%20their%20age%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20physical%20and%20mental%20stamina%20needed%20to%20run%20our%20country.%20We%20need%20you%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20race!%20Thank%20you%20for%20your%20spirit%20and%20determination!%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Fox%20News%2C%20her%20campaign%20has%20received%20an%20over%20200%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20email%20traffic%20from%20supporters%20asking%20the%20candidate%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20race%20following%20former%20president%20Trump's%20primary%20victory%20in%20New%20Hampshire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20six%20days%2C%20the%20campaign%20has%20received%20more%20than%206%2C000%20emails%20total%20with%20messages%20supporting%20the%20former%20South%20Carolina%20governor%20and%20saying%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20the%20real%20Republicans%20only%20chance%20to%20be%20a%20normal%20political%20leader!%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bplease%20do%20not%20quit!%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20news%20channel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20campaign%20has%20been%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20outpouring%20of%20grassroots%20support%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20campaign%20spokesperson%20AnnMarie%20Graham-Barnes%20told%20Fox%20News%20Digital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20political%20establishment%20is%20trying%20to%20coronate%20Trump%2C%20but%20Nikki%20has%20never%20listened%20to%20the%20establishment.%20She%20listens%20to%20Americans%2C%20and%20their%20message%20is%20clear%3A%20Nikki%20is%20the%20last%20one%20standing%20between%20the%20Trump-Biden%20rematch%20that%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20people%20don't%20want%20to%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706667960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F8o0c0lrs_nikki-haley-ani_625x300_16_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-elections-2024-nikki-haley-coins-new-slogan-make-america-normal-again-4964173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian-American%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Nikki%20Haley%20on%20Tuesday%20coined%20a%20new%20slogan%20--%20Make%20America%20Normal%20Again%20--%20as%20her%20campaign%20enters%20the%20critical%20phase%20ahead%20of%20the%20GOP's%20South%20Carolina%20Primary%20on%20February%2023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-elections-2024-nikki-haley-coins-new-slogan-make-america-normal-again-4964173%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-elections-2024-nikki-haley-coins-new-slogan-make-america-normal-again-4964173%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-elections-2024-nikki-haley-coins-new-slogan-make-america-normal-again-4964173%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGill%20Has%20Got%20Cushion%20That%20Even%20Pujara%20Didn't%26quot%3B%3A%20Kumble%20Minces%20No%20Words%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20captain%20Anil%20Kumble%20feels%20that%20the%20embattled%20Shubman%20Gill%20has%20been%20given%20the%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bcushion%26quot%3B%20that%20veteran%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20never%20got%20and%20the%20young%20batter%20needs%20to%20make%20it%20count%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20against%20England%20or%20risk%20being%20under%20tremendous%20pressure.%20The%2024-year-old%20Gill%20has%20not%20scored%20a%20half%20century%20in%20his%20last%2011%20Test%20innings.%20He%20scored%20a%20128%20in%20India's%20first%20innings%20against%20visiting%20Australian%20in%20Ahmedabad%20in%20March%20last%20year%2C%20but%20after%20that%20his%20highest%20score%20has%20been%2036.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%2023%20and%200%20in%20the%20two%20innings%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20England%2C%20which%20India%20lost%20by%2028%20runs%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Gill)%20has%20been%20given%20the%20cushion%20perhaps%20even%20a%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20didn't%20get%2C%20although%20he%20(Pujara)%20has%20played%20over%20a%20100%20Tests%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumble%20said%20on%20'JioCinema'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20keep%20coming%20back%20to%20him%20(Pujara)%20mainly%20because%20that%20was%20his%20place%20(No%203)%20not%20too%20long%20ago.%20Pujara%20played%20in%20that%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20and%20post%20that%2C%20it's%20been%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20who's%20been%20moving%20from%20the%20opener's%20slot%2C%20and%20he%20himself%20wanted%20to%20bat%20at%20No.%203.%26quot%3B%20The%2036-year-old%20Pujara%20last%20played%20a%20Test%20in%20June%202023%20--%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20against%20Australia%20--%20and%20he%20was%20ignored%20after%20that.%20He%20scored%20a%20double%20hundred%20(243%20not%20out)%20in%20a%20Ranji%20match%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20England%20series%2C%20stated%20that%20younger%20players%20were%20being%20preferred%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20look%20ahead%20in%20Indian%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumble%20said%20the%20youngster%20needs%20to%20work%20on%20his%20mindset%20and%20also%20adjust%20his%20technique%20slightly%20for%20the%20second%20Test%20starting%20February%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20when%20you%20want%20to%20bat%20at%20No.%203%20especially%20in%20India%20because%20you%20have%20that%20talent%2C%20you%20certainly%20need%20to%20work%20on%20your%20game.%20He%20has%20the%20skills%2C%20he%20is%20young%20and%20he's%20learning%2C%20but%20he%20needs%20to%20do%20it%20in%20Vizag%20(in%20second%20Test)%2C%20otherwise%20the%20pressure%20will%20be%20on%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20freer%2C%20score%20runs.%20He%20needs%20to%20come%20up%20with%20his%20own%20plan%20to%20tackle%20spin%2C%20because%20he%20has%20hard%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20good%20for%20good%20surfaces%20where%20the%20ball%20is%20coming%20on%20nicely%20and%20the%20faster%20bowlers%20are%20bowling%20at%20you.%20But%20when%20the%20ball%20is%20turning%2C%20when%20it's%20slow%2C%20you%20need%20to%20use%20your%20hands%20and%20control%20and%20check%20your%20shots.%20That's%20something%20he%20needs%20to%20work%20on.%20It%20can't%20be%20one%20flow%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%20But%20can%20Gill%20change%20his%20skill%20sets%20just%20four%20days%20before%20the%20next%20Test%3F%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20all%20the%20mindset.%20You%20can%20certainly%20work%20on%20your%20mindset%2C%20and%20you%20have%20the%20best%20possible%20person%20as%20the%20coach%20(Rahul%20Dravid)%20to%20manage%20that%20for%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20batters%20are%20known%20for%20playing%20spin%20better%20than%20others%20but%20they%20were%20outwitted%20by%20England%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20here.%20Kumble%20advised%20the%20Indians%20to%20think%20out%20of%20the%20box%20in%20the%20remaining%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20certainly%20need%20to%20buckle%20up%20with%20their%20approach%20to%20playing%20against%20spin%20because%20I%20felt%20the%20approach%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20batters%20wasn't%20positive%20and%20even%20the%20footwork%20wasn't%20what%20you%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20felt%20that%20they%20were%20certainly%20rattled%20by%20the%20way%20England%20approached%20their%20batting%20and%20with%20that%2C%20they%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20plans%2C%20some%20unconventional%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumble%20also%20spoke%20on%20wrist%20spinner%20Kuldeep%20Yadav's%20chances%20of%20making%20it%20to%20the%20playing%20XI%20in%20the%20second%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20really%20sure%20whether%20you%20need%20a%20fourth%20spinner.%20But%20if%20India%20feel%20that%20they%20need%20only%20one%20fast%20bowler%2C%20then%20having%20Kuldeep%20will%20certainly%20help.%20He%20will%20have%20variations%20but%20England%20will%20come%20and%20do%20the%20same%20things%20they%20did%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%2