the%20twelfth%20year%20in%20a%20row%20with%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20countries%20scoring%20below%2050.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI%20ranked%20180%20countries%20and%20territories%20by%20their%20perceived%20levels%20of%20public%20sector%20corruption%20on%20a%20scale%20of%20zero%20(highly%20corrupt)%20to%20100%20(very%20clean).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorld's%20Least%20Corrupt%20Countries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenmark%2C%20with%20a%20score%20of%2090%2C%20topped%20the%20index%20for%20the%20sixth%20consecutive%20year%20due%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Bwell-functioning%20justice%20systems%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinland%20(87)%20and%20New%20Zealand%20(85)%20were%20ranked%20second%20and%20third%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorway%20with%20a%20score%20of%2084%2C%20Singapore%20(83)%2C%20Sweden%20(82)%2C%20Switzerland%20(82)%2C%20Netherlands%20(79)%2C%20Germany%20(78)%2C%20and%20Luxembourg%20(78)%20were%20the%20other%20least%20corrupted%20countries%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transparency.org%2Fen%2Fcpi%2F2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20Corruption%20Perceptions%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorld's%20Most%20Corrupt%20Countries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomalia%20with%20a%20score%20of%2011%2C%20Venezuela%20(13)%2C%20Syria%20(13)%2C%20South%20Sudan%20(13)%2C%20and%20Yemen%20(16)%20took%20the%20bottom%20spots%20in%20the%202023%20Corruption%20Perceptions%20Index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20all%20affected%20by%20protracted%20crises%2C%20mostly%20armed%20conflicts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20of%20the%20index%20also%20included%20North%20Korea%20with%20a%20score%20of%20172.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Ranks%2093%20In%20Global%20Corruption%20Index%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20with%20a%20score%20of%2039%2C%20ranked%2093%20on%20the%20corruption%20perceptions%20index%20for%202023%20as%20its%20overall%20score%20remained%20largely%20unchanged%2C%20the%20Transparency%20International%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20overall%20score%20was%2040%20in%202022%20and%20ranked%2085.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%2C%20with%20a%20score%20of%2029%2C%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20(34)%20grappled%20with%20their%20respective%20debt%20burdens%20and%20ensuing%20political%20instability%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202023%20Corruption%20Perceptions%20Index%20was%20based%20on%20perceptions%20of%20public%20sector%20corruption%20and%20used%20data%20from%2013%20external%20sources%2C%20including%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20World%20Economic%20Forum%2C%20private%20risk%20and%20consulting%20companies%2C%20think%20tanks%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706666700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fpi4iaung_corruption-generic_625x300_31_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F2023-corruption-perceptions-index-list-of-worlds-most-and-least-corrupt-countries-released-india-ranks-4964175%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20list%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20corrupt%20countries%20was%20released%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20showed%20that%20most%20of%20the%20nations%20have%20made%20little%20to%20no%20progress%20in%20tackling%20public%20sector%20corruption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F2023-corruption-perceptions-index-list-of-worlds-most-and-least-corrupt-countries-released-india-ranks-4964175%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F2023-corruption-perceptions-index-list-of-worlds-most-and-least-corrupt-countries-released-india-ranks-4964175%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F2023-corruption-perceptions-index-list-of-worlds-most-and-least-corrupt-countries-rele