ns%20submitted%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegistrations%20will%20now%20be%20selected%20based%20on%20unique%20beneficiaries%2C%20reducing%20the%20potential%20for%20fraud%20and%20ensuring%20equal%20chances%20of%20selection.%20Beginning%20with%20the%20FY%202025%20initial%20registration%20period%2C%20USCIS%20will%20mandate%20registrants%20to%20provide%20valid%20passport%20information%20or%20valid%20travel%20document%20information%20for%20each%20beneficiary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20rule%20clarifies%20requirements%20regarding%20the%20requested%20employment%20start%20date%20on%20certain%20petitions%20subject%20to%20the%20H-1B%20cap%2C%20allowing%20filing%20with%20requested%20start%20dates%20after%20October%201%20of%20the%20relevant%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20codifies%20USCIS'%20ability%20to%20deny%20or%20revoke%20H-1B%20petitions%20if%20the%20registration%20contains%20false%20attestation%20or%20is%20otherwise%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSCIS%20has%20also%20announced%20a%20Fee%20Schedule%20final%20rule%2C%20effective%20after%20the%20initial%20registration%20period%20for%20FY%202025%20H-1B%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20registration%20period%20for%20the%20FY%202025%20H-1B%20cap%20will%20open%20on%20March%206%2C%202024%2C%20and%20run%20through%20March%2022%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSCIS%20will%20launch%20organisational%20accounts%20on%20February%2028%2C%202024%2C%20allowing%20collaboration%20on%20H-1B%20registrations%2C%20petitions%2C%20and%20associated%20forms.%20Online%20filing%20of%20Form%20I-129%20and%20Form%20I-907%20for%20non-cap%20H-1B%20petitions%20will%20also%20commence%20on%20the%20same%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20petitioners%20can%20continue%20to%20file%20paper%20Form%20I-129%20H-1B%20petitions%2C%20online%20filing%20options%20will%20be%20available%20starting%20April%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSCIS%20Director%20Ur%20M%20Jaddou%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20improvements%20in%20th