%2F107274865.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107274865.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbrain-computer-interface-chip-has-been-placed-in-a-human-musk%2Farticleshow%2F107274865.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbrain-computer-interface-chip-has-been-placed-in-a-human-musk%2Famp_articleshow%2F107274865.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbrain-computer-interface-chip-has-been-placed-in-a-human-musk%2Famp_articleshow%2F107274865.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-Origin%20Couple%20Jailed%20In%20UK%20For%20Exporting%20Cocaine%20To%20Australia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian-origin%20couple%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20whose%20extradition%20was%20sought%20by%20India%20on%20charges%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20their%20adopted%20son%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%2033%20years%20in%20prison%20each%20after%20being%20convicted%20of%20exporting%20more%20than%20half%20a%20tonne%20of%20cocaine%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArti%20Dhir%2C%2059%2C%20and%20Kavaljitsinh%20Raijada%2C%2035%2C%20from%20Hanwell%20in%20Ealing%20were%20identified%20by%20the%20National%20Crime%20Agency%20(NCA)%20investigators%20after%20Australian%20Border%20Force%20intercepted%20the%20cocaine%20worth%2057%20million%20pounds%20upon%20its%20arrival%20in%20Sydney%20in%20May%202021%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20behind%20a%20front%20company%20that%20had%20sent%20the%20drugs%20by%20plane%20under%20a%20cover%20load%20of%20metal%20toolboxes%2C%20according%20to%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge's%20commendations%20were%20awarded%20to%20three%20NCA%20officers%20who%20worked%20on%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhir%20and%20Raijada%20denied%20exporting%20cocaine%20to%20Australia%20and%20money%20laundering.%20They%20were%20convicted%20of%2012%20counts%20of%20exportation%20and%2018%20counts%20of%20money%20laundering%20by%20a%20jury%20following%20a%20trial%20at%20Southwark%20Crown%20Court%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20sentenced%20at%20the%20same%20court%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drugs%20exported%20by%20the%20two%20had%20been%20shipped%20via%20a%20commercial%20flight%20from%20the%20UK%20and%20consisted%20of%20six%20metal%20toolboxes%20which%2C%20when%20opened%2C%20were%20found%20to%20contain%20514%20kilograms%20of%20cocaine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drugs%20would%20have%20been%20worth%20up%20to%2057%20million%20pounds%20when%20sold%20in%20Australia%2C%20where%20prices%20are%20significantly%20higher%20than%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20UK%2C%20a%20kilo%20of%20cocaine%20at%20wholesale%20is%20priced%20around%2026%2C000%20pound%20but%20in%20Australia%20the%20same%20amount%20sells%20for%20110%2C000%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficers%20traced%20the%20consignment%20back%20to%20Dhir%20and%20Raijada%2C%20who%20had%20set%20up%20a%20front%20company%20called%20Viefly%20Freight%20Services%20with%20the%20sole%20purpose%20of%20smuggling%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20defendants%20had%20been%20directors%20of%20the%20company%20at%20different%20points%20since%20its%20incorporation%20in%20June%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaijada's%20fingerprints%20were%20found%20on%20the%20plastic%20wrappings%20of%20the%20metal%20toolboxes%20containing%20the%20seized%20drugs%2C%20while%20receipts%20for%20the%20order%20of%20the%20toolboxes%2C%20worth%202855%20pounds%20were%20discovered%20at%20the%20couple's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCA's%20case%20was%20that%20there%20had%20been%2037%20consignments%20sent%20to%20Australia%20since%20June%202019%2C%20of%20which%2022%20were%20dummy%20runs%20and%2015%20contained%20cocaine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhir%20had%20been%20employed%20by%20a%20flight%20services%20company%20at%20Heathrow%20from%20March%202003%20until%20October%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaijada%20worked%20at%20the%20same%20company%20from%20March%202014%20to%20December%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCA%20investigators%20believe%20that%20their%20knowledge%20of%20the%20airport%20freight%20procedures%20was%20used%20to%20cover%20their%20criminal%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhir%20and%20Raijada%20were%20arrested%20at%20their%20home%20in%20Hanwell%20on%20June%2021%2C%202021.%20and%20officers%20seized%205000%20pounds%20worth%20of%20gold-plated%20silver%20bars%2C%2013%2C000%20pounds%20inside%20the%20home%20and%20found%2060%2C000%20pounds%20in%20cash%20in%20a%20safety%20deposit%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20further%20investigations%2C%20the%20pair%20were%20arrested%20again%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCA%20officers%20discovered%20almost%203%20million%20pounds%20in%20cash%20hidden%20in%20boxes%20and%20suitcases%20at%20a%20storage%20unit%20in%20Hanwell%2C%20which%20Raijada%20had%20rented%20in%20his%20mother's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinancial%20inquiries%20found%20they%20had%20also%20purchased%20a%20flat%20in%20Ealing%20for%20800%2C000%20pounds%20and%20a%20Land%20Rover%20for%2062%2C000%20pounds%2C%20despite%20declaring%20profits%20of%20only%20a%20few%20thousand%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20showed%20that%20both%20defendants%20held%20cash%20in%20bank%20accounts%20which%20far%20exceeded%20their%20declared%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20deposited%20almost%20740%2C000%20pounds%20in%20cash%20into%2022%20different%20bank%20accounts%20since%202019%20and%20were%20further%20charged%20with%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCA%20will%20now%20start%20Proceeds%20of%20Crime%20proceedings%20against%20both%20defendants%20to%20strip%20them%20of%20their%20assets%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPiers%20Phillips%2C%20NCA%20Senior%20Investigating%20Officer%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BArti%20Dhir%20and%20Kavaljitsinh%20Raijada%20used%20their%20insider%20knowledge%20of%20the%20air%20freight%20industry%20to%20traffic%20cocaine%20worth%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20pounds%20from%20the%20UK%20to%20Australia%2C%20where%20they%20knew%20they%20could%20maximise%20their%20revenue.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThey%20kept%20their%20illicit%20profits%20in%20cash%20at%20their%20home%20and%20in%20storage%20units%2C%20as%20well%20as%20purchasing%20property%2C%20gold%20and%20silver%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20hide%20their%20wealth.%20These%20defendants%20may%20have%20thought%20they%20were%20removed%20from%20the%20misery%20caused%20by%20the%20drugs%20trade%20but%20their%20greed%20was%20fuelling%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Philips%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NCA%20worked%20closely%20with%20our%20partners%20in%20Australia%20and%20UK%20Border%20Force%20to%20dismantle%20the%20supply%20chain%20created%20by%20Dhir%20and%20Raijada%20and%20bring%20them%20to%20justice.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20target%20class%20A%20drugs%20supply%20and%20the%20criminals%20overseeing%20it%2C%20both%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20overseas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20investigator%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20allegations%20against%20the%20couple%20relate%20to%20their%2011-year-old%20adopted%20son%20Gopal%20Sejani%20and%20his%20brother-in-law%20Harsukhbhai%20Kardani%20in%20February%202017%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20by%20Gujarat%20police%20claimed%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20hatched%20a%20plot%20to%20adopt%20Gopal%20and%20then%20insure%20him%20for%20around%20Rs%201.3%20crore%20before%20staging%20his%20kidnapping%20and%20murder%20in%20India%20to%20split%20the%20life%20insurance%20payout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20extradition%20request%20for%20the%20duo%20had%20been%20turned%20down%20by%20Westminster%20Magistrates'%20Court%20in%20Lon