indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107271579.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMasaba%20Gupta%2C%20a%20designer-actor%2C%20praised%20Vikrant%20Massey's%20performance%20in%20'12th%20Fail'%20on%20Instagram.%20Massey%20thanked%20her%20for%20always%20praying%20for%20him.%20Massey%2C%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20expressed%20how%20deeply%20moved%20he%20was%20after%20reading%20the%20script.%20The%20film%20has%20received%20an%20overwhelming%20response%20at%20the%20box%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmasaba-gupta-praises-childhood-friend-vikrant-massey-for-his-performance-in-12th-fail%2Farticleshow%2F107271579.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20A%20Picnic%20Spot%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%20Over%20Non-Hindus'%20Entry%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Temples%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Madras%20High%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20directed%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20HR%26amp%3BCE%20department%20to%20install%20boards%20in%20all%20Hindu%20temples%20stating%20non-Hindus%20were%20not%20permitted%20beyond%20the%20'Kodimaram'%20(flagpole)%20area%20in%20the%20respective%20shrines%20and%20said%20Hindus%20also%20have%20fundamental%20right%20to%20profess%20and%20practice%20their%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20S%20Srimathy%20of%20the%20HC's%20Madurai%20Bench%20gave%20the%20judgement%20while%20hearing%20a%20plea%20from%20D%20Senthilkumar%2C%20who%20sought%20directions%20to%20the%20respondents%20to%20permit%20Hindus%20alone%20to%20the%20Arulmigu%20Palani%20Dhandayuthapani%20Swamy%20temple%20and%20its%20sub%20temples.%20He%20also%20wanted%20that%20display%20boards%20to%20that%20effect%20in%20all%20entrances%20be%20set%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20famous%20Lord%20Murugan%20temple%20is%20located%20in%20Palani%20in%20Dindigul%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20respondents%20were%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%2C%20represented%20by%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20Department%20of%20Tourism%2C%20Culture%20and%20Religious%20Endowments%2C%20The%20Commissioner%2C%20Hindu%20Religious%20and%20Charitable%20Endowments%20Department%20(HR%26amp%3BCE)%20and%20the%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20the%20Palani%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HR%26amp%3BCE%20department%20administers%20Hindu%20temples%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmitting%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20court%20directed%20the%20respondents%20to%20install%20boards%20indicating%20%26quot%3Bnon-Hindus%20are%20not%20allowed%20inside%20temple%20after%20Kodimaram%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20temples%2C%20near%20the%20flagpole%20and%20at%20prominent%20places%20in%20the%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20respondents%20are%20directed%20not%20to%20allow%20the%20non-Hindus%20who%20do%20not%20believe%20in%20Hindu%20religion.%20If%20any%20Non-Hindu%20claims%20to%20visit%20particular%20deity%20in%20the%20temple%2C%20then%20the%20respondents%20shall%20obtain%20undertaking%20from%20the%20said%20non-Hindu%20that%20he%20is%20having%20faith%20in%20the%20deity%20and%20he%20would%20follow%20the%20customs%20and%20practices%20of%20Hindu%20religion%20and%20also%20abide%20by%20the%20temple%20customs%20and%20on%20such%20undertaking%20the%20said%20non-Hindu%20may%20be%20allowed%20to%20visit%20the%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20ruled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20whenever%20a%20such%20a%20person%20is%20allowed%20based%20on%20the%20undertaking%20the%20same%20shall%20be%20entered%20in%20the%20register%20which%20shall%20be%20maintained%20by%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20respondents%20shall%20maintain%20the%20temple%20premises%20by%20strictly%20following%20the%20agamas%20(temple%20rules)%2C%20customs%20and%20practices%20of%20the%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20respondents%20submitted%20the%20said%20writ%20petition%20was%20filed%20only%20for%20the%20Palani%20temple%20and%20the%20order%20may%20be%20restricted%20to%20it%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20issue%20raised%20is%20larger%20issue%20and%20the%20same%20ought%20to%20be%20applicable%20to%20all%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20hence%20the%20plea%20of%20the%20respondents%20is%20rejected.%20As%20stated%20supra%20these%20restrictions%20would%20ensure%20communal%20harmony%20among%20different%20religions%20and%20ensure%20peace%20in%20the%20society.%20Therefore%20the%20State%20Government%2C%20the%20HR%26amp%3BCE%20department%2C%20the%20respondents%20and%20all%20persons%20who%20are%20involved%20in%20temple%20administration%20are%20directed%20to%20follow%20the%20directions%20to%20all%20Hindu%20temples%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20belonging%20to%20Hindu%20religion%20have%20right%20to%20profess%20and%20practice%20the%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLikewise%2C%20people%20belonging%20to%20other%20religions%20have%20right%20to%20profess%20and%20practice%20their%20religion.%20But%20the%20customs%20and%20practice%20of%20their%20respective%20religion%20cannot%20be%20interfering%20with%20and%20any%20interference%20ought%20to%20be%20curtailed.%20The%20temple%20is%20not%20(a)%20picnic%20spot%20or%20tourist%20spot.%20Even%20in%20Arulmighu%20Brahadeeswarar%20Temple%2C%20Thanjavur%20the%20other%20religion%20people%20are%20allowed%20to%20admire%20and%20appreciate%20the%20architectural%20monuments%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20but%20not%20after%20Kodimaram.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhile%20admiring%20the%20architectural%20monuments%20the%20people%20cannot%20use%20the%20premises%20as%20picnic%20spot%20or%20tourist%20spot%20and%20the%20temples%20premises%20ought%20to%20be%20maintained%20with%20reverence%20and%20as%20per%20agamas.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20rights%20guaranteed%20under%20the%20Articles%20is%20not%20granting%20any%20right%20to%20the%20respondents%20to%20allow%20the%20other%20religion%20people%20if%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20faith%20and%20belief%20in%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20rights%20are%20guaranteed%20to%20all%20religions%20and%20there%20cannot%20be%20any%20bias%20in%20applying%20such%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20also%20referred%20to%20certain%20incidents%20of%20non-Hindus%20allegedly%20entering%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20also%20reported%20that%20in%20Arulmighu%20Brahadeeswarar%20Temple%20a%20group%20of%20persons%20belonging%20to%20other%20religion%20had%20treated%20the%20temple%20premises%20as%20picnic%20spot%20and%20had%20non%20vegetarian%20food%20inside%20the%20temple%20premises.%20Likewise%2C%20recently%20on%2011.01.2024%20a%20newspaper%20had%20reported%20that%20a%20group%20of%20persons%20belonging%20to%20the%20other%20religion%20had%20entered%20the%20Arulmighu%20Meenakshi%20Sundareswarar%20Temple%2C%20Madurai%20with%20%26quot%3Btheir%20sacred%20book%26quot%3B%20near%20sanctum%20and%20sanctorum%20and%20was%20attempting%20to%20do%20their%20prayers%26quot%3B%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20incidents%20are%20absolutely%20interfering%20with%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20guaranteed%20to%20the%20Hindus%20under%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Hindus%20also%20have%20fundamental%20right%20to%20profess%20and%20practice%20their%20religion%20freely%20and%20propagate%20their%20religion%20without%20interfering%20in%20their%20way%20of%20practice.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Hindus%20have%20right%20to%20maintain%20their%20temples%20as%20per%20their%20customs%2C%20practices%20and%20Hindu%20Religious%20and%20Charitable%20Endowment%20Department%20is%20having%20duty%20to%20protect%20the%20temples%20from%20such%20unwanted%20incidents.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20in%20the%20above%20narrated%20incidents%20the%20Department%20had%20failed%20to%20protect%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20guaranteed%20under%20the%20constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706641800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fq1v460s_madras-high-court_625x300_29_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fmadras-high-court-to-tamil-nadu-cant-allow-non-hindus-beyond-flagpole-in-temples-4962278%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madras%20High%20Court%20directed%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20HR%26amp%3BCE%20department%20to%20install%20boards%20in%20all%20Hindu%20temples%20stating%20non-Hindus%20were%20not%20permitted%20beyond%20the%20'Kodimaram'%20(flagpole)%20area%20in%20the%20respective%20shrines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fmadras-high-court-to-tamil-nadu-cant-allow-non-hindus-beyond-flagpole-in-temples-4962278%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fmadras-high-court-to-tamil-nadu-cant-allow-non-hindus-beyond-flagpole-in-temples-4962278%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fmadras-high-court-to-tamil-nadu-cant-allow-non-hindus-beyond-flagpole-in-temples-4962278%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fast-track%20court%20also%20says%20unseal%20ASI%20report%20on%20Gyanvapi%20study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706641800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107271474%2Cimgsize-2278158.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvaranasi%2Ffast-track-court-also-says-unseal-asi-report-on-gyanvapi-study%2Farticleshow%2F107271474.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Varanasi%20fast-track%20court%20of%20civil%20judge%20(senior%20division)%20Prashant%20Kumar%