2%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hemant%20Soren's%20Wife%20May%20Be%20Named%20Chief%20Minister%20If%20He's%20Arrested%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren's%20wife%20Kalpana%20Soren%20might%20step%20into%20his%20shoes%20if%20he%20gets%20arrested%2C%20sources%20in%20his%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20Party%20have%20claimed.%20Mr%20Soren%20will%20be%20questioned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20tomorrow%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case.%20There%20are%20chances%20that%20he%20might%20be%20arrested%20by%20the%20agency%20after%20his%20statement%20is%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%2C%20say%20sources%2C%20made%20the%20announcement%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20MLAs%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20this%20evening.%20The%20MLAs%20have%20agreed%20since%20preservation%20of%20the%20government%20is%20crucial%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%2C%20all%20the%20MLAs%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20of%20Congress%2C%20are%20fully%20supporting%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20Banna%20Gupta%2C%20the%20state's%20health%20minister%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20told%20reporters%20late%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20however%2C%20might%20be%20a%20legal%20hurdle%20in%20Mrs%20Soren%20taking%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstitutional%20provisions%20demand%20that%20if%20the%20term%20of%20the%20Assembly%20will%20expire%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%2C%20by-polls%20cannot%20be%20held.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20for%20Kalpana%20Soren%20to%20become%20an%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20election%20in%20Jharkhand%20is%20due%20in%20November%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20needed%2C%20legal%20opinion%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20this%20matter%20or%20someone%20else%20will%20take%20over%20at%20the%20top%20post%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rs%20600-crore%20land%20scam%20involves%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20racket%26quot%3B%20to%20change%20of%20ownership%20of%20government%20land%2C%20which%20was%20subsequently%20sold%20to%20builders%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20has%20so%20far%20arrested%2014%20people%20in%20the%20case%2C%20including%202011-batch%20IAS%20officer%20Chhavi%20Ranjan%20who%20served%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20state%20Social%20Welfare%20Department%20and%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20has%20claimed%20that%20he%20is%20the%20target%20of%20a%20huge%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706640120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0hfeokf_kalpana-soren-hemant-soren-ani_625x300_30_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-sorens-wife-may-be-named-chief-minister-if-hes-arrested-sources-4962510%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren's%20wife%20Kalpana%20Soren%20might%20step%20into%20his%20shoes%20if%20he%20gets%20arrested%2C%20sources%20in%20his%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20Party%20have%20claimed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-sorens-wife-may-be-named-chief-minister-if-hes-arrested-sources-4962510%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-sorens-wife-may-be-named-chief-minister-if-hes-arrested-sources-4962510%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-sorens-wife-may-be-named-chief-minister-if-hes-arrested-sources-4962510%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iqra%20Aziz's%20wedding%20outfit%20is%20inspired%20by%20PC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706639591000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107271035%2Cimgsize-69340.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3