t%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20addressed%20his%20first%20rally%20in%20Bihar%20since%20the%202020%20assembly%20polls%20campaign%2C%20also%20recounted%20a%20joke%2C%20now%20popular%20on%20social%20media%2C%20about%20which%20he%20learnt%20from%20former%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Singh%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joke%2C%20which%20was%20also%20shared%20by%20AICC%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20on%20X%20the%20day%20before%2C%20says%20Kumar%20had%20returned%20to%20Raj%20Bhavan%20to%20collect%20his%20shawl%2Fmuffler%20after%20being%20sworn%20in%20for%20a%20record%20ninth%20time%2C%20causing%20the%20Governor%20to%20wonder%20if%20the%20JD(U)%20supremo%20was%20back%20to%20take%20oath%20as%20leader%20of%20a%20different%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%20which%20lasted%20around%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20aim%20is%20to%20ensure%20justice%2C%20both%20social%20and%20economic.%20For%20social%20justice%2C%20we%20call%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20which%20is%20like%20the%20X-ray%20of%20the%20society.%20Once%20that%20is%20done%20we%20can%20go%20for%20an%20MRI%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20highlighted%20the%20fact%20that%20OBCs%2C%20despite%20their%20huge%20representation%2C%20were%20grossly%20under-represented%20in%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20corporate%20houses%20and%20%26quot%3Beven%20in%20the%20media%2C%20they%20are%20rarely%20allowed%20to%20rise%20beyond%20the%20position%20of%20reporters%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20rally%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20Nitish%20ji%20that%20he%20will%20have%20to%20get%20caste%20survey%20done.%20We%20will%20give%20him%20no%20concessions.%20Buckling%20under%20pressure%2C%20he%20struck%20a%20compromise%20with%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20always%20been%20against%20social%20justice.%20He%20got%20scared%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20be%20afraid.%26quot%3B%20Like%20social%20justice%2C%20economic%20justice%20is%20also%20essential%2C%20he%20said%20and%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20'makhana'%20(fox%20nuts)%20which%20is%20grown%20in%20abundance%20in%20Purnea%20and%20adjoining%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20towards%20a%2010-kg%20garland%20made%20of%20'makhana'%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20know%20that%20this%20can%20fetch%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20in%20American%20markets.%20But%20the%20farmers%20who%20cultivated%20these%20would%20be%20getting%20not%20more%20than%20Rs%202%2C500.%20We%20want%20this%20to%20change%20and%20the%20farmers%20to%20get%20their%20due.%26quot%3B%20The%20former%20Congress%20president%2C%20who%20is%20leading%20the%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%20which%20commenced%20earlier%20this%20month%20from%20Manipur%2C%20also%20expressed%20dismay%20at%20the%20ethnic%20situation%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state%2C%20claiming%20the%20situation%20there%20resembled%20'a%20civil%20war'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20was%20also%20supposed%20to%20be%20addressed%20by%20AICC%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20who%20was%20denied%20permission%20to%20land%20his%20chartered%20flight%20at%20a%20nearby%20airstrip%2C%20on%20account%20of%20bad%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20president%20Akhilesh%20Prasad%20Singh%20played%20a%20video%20message%20from%20the%20party%20president%2C%20after%20alleging%20%26quot%3BKharge%20has%20been%20prevented%20from%20coming%20here%20just%20like%20our%20allies%2C%20RJD%20leaders%20Lalu%20Prasad%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20You%20can%20see%20bright%20sunlight%20all%20around.%20But%20the%20Defence%20ministry%20which%20controls%20the%20airstrip%20here%20denied%20permission%20to%20our%20party%20president%20claiming%20visibility%20was%20poor.%26quot%3B%20Prasad%2C%20the%20RJD's%20founding%20president%2C%20who%20is%20in%20his%2070s%20and%20suffers%20from%20various%20ailments%2C%20was%20in%20Patna%2C%20where%20he%20had%20been%20grilled%20for%20nine%20hours%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20the%20day%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%2C%20his%20son%20and%20heir%20apparent%2C%20was%20being%20questioned%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20the%20alleged%20land-for-jobs%20scam%20in%20which%20the%20father-son%20duo%20and%20many%20others%20close%20to%20them%20are%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20Congress%20leaders%20who%20addressed%20the%20rally%20included%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accompanying%20Gandhi%20during%20the%20Yatra%2C%20former%20Union%20minister%20Tariq%20Anwar%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Imran%20Pratapgarhi%20and%20former%20JNU%20students'%20union%20president%20Kanhaiya%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20number%20of%20drones%20were%20intercepted%20by%20security%20personnel%20at%20the%20Rangbhoomi%20Maidan%2C%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seized%20nine%20drones.%20The%20matter%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20and%20investigations%20will%20be%20launched%20as%20per%20his%20instruction%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anil%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20SHO%20of%20K-hat%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20Yatra%20had%20entered%20Bihar%20on%20Monday%20from%20Kishanganj%20district%20and%20it%20reached%20Purnea%20after%20a%20night%20halt%20at%20Araria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20addressing%20the%20rally%20in%20Purnia%20where%20Gandhi%20also%20interacted%20with%20local%20farmers%2C%20the%20entourage%20left%20for%20neighbouring%20Katihar%20from%20where%20it%20is%20scheduled%20to%20leave%20for%20Malda%20in%20West%20Bengal%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706637420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F20