nt%20diplomatic%20disputes%20between%20relevant%20countries.%20The%20information%20released%20by%20Pakistan%20is%20worth%20our%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fxwfw_665399%2Fs2510_665401%2F202401%2Ft20240130_11236316.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Wang%20Wenbin%20said%20at%20a%20daily%20media%20briefing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20China%20%E2%80%9Cfirmly%20opposes%20double%20standards%20on%20counterterrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CChina%20stands%20for%20strengthening%20counterterrorism%20cooperation%20among%20all%20countries%20to%20jointly%20fight%20all%20forms%20of%20terrorism%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20the%20Chinese%20diplomat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECiting%20the%20allegations%20by%20Canada%20and%20US%20of%20the%20activities%20of%20Indian%20agents%20against%20separatists%20on%20their%20soil%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20secretary%20claimed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20network%20of%20extra-judicial%20and%20extra-territorial%20killings%20has%20become%20a%20global%20phenomenon%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20reaction%2C%20India%20claimed%20that%20it%20is%20Pakistan%20that%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20epicentre%20of%20terrorism%2C%20organised%20crime%2C%20and%20illegal%20transnational%20activities%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20and%20many%20other%20countries%20have%20publicly%20warned%20Pakistan%20cautioning%20that%20it%20would%20be%20consumed%20by%20its%20own%20culture%20of%20terror%20and%20violence.%20Pakistan%20will%20reap%20what%20it%20sows.%20To%20blame%20others%20for%20its%20own%20misdeeds%20can%20neither%20be%20a%20justification%20nor%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Indian%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20India%20has%20not%20reacted%20to%20the%20Chinese%20statement%20yet%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20happy%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20has%20several%20times%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-again-puts-technical-hold-on-unsc-sanctioning-jems-rauf-azhar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eput%20a%20hold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20India-backed%20proposals%20to%20list%20Pakistan-based%20terrorists%20at%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%E2%80%99s%20sanctions%20committee%2C%20which%20had%20led%20New%20Delhi%20to%20accuse%20Beijing%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Funsc-india-china-blacklist-abdul-rauf-azhar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edoublespeak%20and%20double%20standards%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20fighting%20terrorism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706637035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F31140436%2Fimage-871.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-on-pakistans-allegations-indian-involvement-in-killing-its-citizens%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Last%20week%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20secretary%20Muhammad%20Syrus%20Sajjad%20Qazi%20had%20asserted%20that%20an%20investigation%20had%20uncovered%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20linking%20two%20Indian%20agents%20to%20the%20murders%20of%20two%20Pakistani%20citizens%20in%20September%20and%20October%202023.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-on-pakistans-allegations-indian-involvement-in-killing-its-citizens%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jacqueline%20Fernandez%20Used%2C%20Enjoyed%20Conman's%20Gains%20From%20Crime%3A%20Probe%20Agency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBollywood%20actor%20Jacqueline%20Fernandez%2C%20accused%20in%20a%20Rs%20200-crore%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20was%20knowingly%20involved%20in%20the%20possession%20and%20use%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20of%20alleged%20conman%20Sukesh%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20has%20contended%20before%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20contention%20was%20made%20in%20an%20affidavit%20filed%20in%20response%20to%20Ms%20Fernandez's%20plea%20seeking%20quashing%20of%20an%20FIR%20against%20her%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20allegedly%20involving%20Chandrasekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20was%20listed%20before%20Justice%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Ohri%20and%20the%20counsel%20representing%20Ms%20Fernandez%20sought%20time%20to%20file%20a%20rejoinder%20in%20response%20to%20the%20ED's%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20hearing%20on%20April%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20reply%2C%20ED%20claimed%20Ms%20Fernandez%20never%20revealed%20the%20truth%20regarding%20the%20financial%20transactions%20with%20Chandrasekhar%20and%20always%20concealed%20facts%20until%20confronted%20with%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20continues%20to%20hold%20back%20the%20truth%20even%20till%20date.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20Fernandez%20wiped%20out%20the%20entire%20data%20from%20her%20mobile%20phone%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20thereby%20tampering%20with%20the%20evidence.%20She%20also%20asked%20her%20colleagues%20to%20destroy%20the%20evidence.%20Evidence%20proves%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20she%20had%20been%20enjoying%2C%20using%20and%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%20Thus%2C%20it%20is%20proved%20that%20Fernandez%20was%20knowingly%20involved%20in%20the%20possession%20and%20use%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20of%20accused%20Chandrasekhar%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20initially%20in%20her%20statements%2C%20the%20actor%20tried%20to%20cover%20up%20her%20conduct%20by%20claiming%20that%20she%20has%20been%20the%20victim%20of%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20however%2C%20during%20investigation%2C%20she%20failed%20to%20provide%20any%20substantial%20material%20to%20establish%20victimisation%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20she%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20criminal%20antecedents%20of%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20still%20she%20continued%20to%20receive%2C%20enjoy%20and%20possess%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20for%20herself%20and%20her%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20said%20initially%20Fernandez%20did%20not%20admit%20to%20receiving%20huge%20sums%20of%20money%20and%20valuable%20gifts%20from%20him%20for%20her%20family%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20and%20added%20that%20these%20luxury%20items%20were%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20being%20generated%20out%20of%20criminal%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20submission%20of%20Ms%20Fernandez%20that%20she%20has%20been%20presented%20as%20a%20prosecution%20witness%20in%20the%20predicate%20offence%20in%20which%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20by%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20cannot%20be%20made%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20the%20ED%20said%20the%20definition%20of%20the%20offence%20of%20money%20laundering%20does%20not%20stipulate%20that%20to%20trigger%20section%203%20of%20PMLA%2C%20a%20person%20should%20also%20be%20proved%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20predicate%20offence%20besides%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20offence%20of%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20said%20Ms%20Fernandez%20was%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20criminal%20antecedents%20of%20Chandrasekhar%20and%20also%20the%20fact%20that%20Leena%20Maria%20Paul%20is%20his%20wife%20but%20despite%20this%2C%20she%20continued%20the%20relationship%20with%20him%20and%20also%20received%20financial%20benefits%20from%20him%20which%20are%20nothing%20but%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20also%20opposed%20the%20petition%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20maintainability%2C%20saying%20a%20special%20court%20has%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20prosecution%20complaint%20(chargesheet)%20and%20taken%20a%20view%20that%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20is%20made%20out%20to%20be%20proceeded%20with%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20challenge%20to%20the%20cognisance%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Fernandez%20said%20in%20her%20plea%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20outset%20it%20is%20submitted%20that%20evidence%20filed%20by%20the%20ED%20would%20prove%20that%20the%20petitioner%20(Fernandez)%20is%20an%20innocent%20victim%20of%20Chandrasekhar's%20maliciously%20targeted%20attack.%20There%20is%20absolutely%20no%20indication%20that%20she%20had%20any%20involvement%20whatsoever%20in%20aiding%20him%20to%20launder%20his%20purportedly%20ill-gotten%20wealth.%20Hence%2C%20she%20cannot%20be%20prosecuted%20for%20the%20offences%20under%20Sections%203%20and%204%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20prosecution%20complaint%20filed%20against%20her%20confirmed%20that%20nowhere%20it%20has%20been%20alleged%20that%20she%20had%20the%20knowledge%20about%20the%20nefarious%20activities%20of%20Chandrasekhar%20in%20extorting%20money%20from%20complainant%20Aditi%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20complaint%20is%20silent%20about%20even%20a%20remote%20allegation%20of%20knowledge%20as%20attributed%20to%20the%20petitioner.%20It%20is%20impossible%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20petitioner%20knowingly%20engaged%20in%20any%20of%20the%20activities%20that%20is%20today%20punished%20by%20Section%203%20of%20the%20PMLA%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20she%20had%20no%20knowledge%20whatsoever%20of%20the%20predicate%20offence%20--%20the%20main%20offence%20of%20extortion%20--%20committed%20by%20Chandrasekhar%20and%20his%20associates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20the%20ED%20has%20acted%20in%20a%20partisan%20manner%20while%20arraigning%20her%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ED%20has%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20Nora%20Fatehi%20(another%20Bollywood%20actor)%20despite%20it%20being%20an%20admitted%20fact%20on%20record%20that%20her%20family%20member%20received%20a%20BMW%20car%20from%20Sukesh%20Chandrasekhar%20on%20her%20instructions.%20It%20is%20of%20importance%20to%20note%20that%20the%20fact%20of%20Nora%20Fatehi%20receiving%20gifts%20from%20Sukesh%20Chandrasekhar%20has%20been%20presented%20to%20ED%20under%20the%20head%20'dissipation%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime'%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20submitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Fernandez%20has%20appeared%20before%20the%20ED%20for%20questioning%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20investigation%20against%20Chandrasekhar%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20earlier%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20Chandrasekhar%20for%20allegedly%20duping%20the%20spouses%20of%20former%20promoters%20of%20Ranbaxy%20--%20Shivinder%20Singh%20and%20Malvinder%20Singh%20--%20of%20Rs%20200%20crore.%20There%20are%20other%20ongoing%20investigations%20against%20him%20in%20several%20cases%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrasekhar%20and%20his%20wife%20Leena%20Maria%20Paul%2C%20facing%20proceedings%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20registered%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20were%20earlier%20arrested%20by%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20along%20with%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20also%20invoked%20the%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20(MCOCA)%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20alleged%20that%20Paul%20and%20Chandrasekhar%20along%20with%20others%20used%20hawala%20routes%20and%20created%20shell%20companies%20to%20park%20the%20money%20earned%20as%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%