20Social%20Justice%2C%20Says%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Exited%20through%20'Backdoor'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F26210652%2FFufcgtmX0AQCmkG.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20paid%20tribute%20to%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20on%20Martyrs%E2%80%99%20Day%2C%20the%20day%20to%20mark%20the%20Mahatma%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20in%201948%2C%20at%20the%20campsite%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20Araria%20district%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20broke%20his%20silence%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20flip-flop%20back%20into%20the%20BJP%20camp%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Purnea.%20He%20started%20with%20the%20now%20well-known%20joke%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20forgetting%20his%20shawl%20at%20Raj%20Bhawan%20after%20presenting%20himself%20to%20reconstitute%20his%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%20this%20time.%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Chhatisgarh%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20had%20just%20narrated%20the%20joke%20to%20him.%20The%20joke%20goes%20that%20when%20Kumar%20turned%20up%20to%20pick%20up%20his%20shawl%2C%20the%20governor%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eitni%20jaldi%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20(back%20so%20soon%20to%20again%20change%20camps%3F).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joke%20got%20many%20laughs%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20underlined%20that%20INDIA%20would%20continue%20to%20stand%20for%20backward%20classes%20and%20for%20social%20justice%20in%20Bihar.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-reaches-purnia-on-day-2-in-bihar-rahul-to-address-rally%2Farticle67791928.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20said%20the%20alliance%20does%20not%20need%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20for%20the%20cause.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%E2%80%98Mahagathbandhan%E2%80%99%20(grand%20alliance)%20will%20fight%20for%20social%20justice%20in%20Bihar%3B%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20Nitish%20Kumar%20for%20that%20purpose%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20him%20at%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20leader%20is%20reported%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-3DtTN85FoU%3Fsi%3DAxxwPUkwZmHKQWFj%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20India%20%E2%80%9Cneeds%20a%20caste-based%20census%20to%20determine%20the%20exact%20population%20of%20Dalits%2C%20OBCs%20and%20others%E2%80%9D.%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20repeating%20the%20metaphor%20of%20%E2%80%9CX-ray%20of%20the%20population%E2%80%9D%2C%20to%20determine%20exactly%20what%20ails%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20left%20the%20alliance%20due%20to%20his%20inability%20to%20stomach%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20caste%20survey%20and%20used%20the%20BJP%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbackdoor%E2%80%9D%20to%20exit%20the%20situation.%20%E2%80%9CUnderstand%20why%20Nitish%20Ji%20got%20stuck.%20I%20told%20him%20straight%20that%20%E2%80%98you%20will%20have%20to%20conduct%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99.%20And%20we%20(Congress)%2C%20along%20with%20RJD%2C%20insisted%20on%20Nitish%20ji%20conducting%20the%20survey.%20But%20the%20BJP%20got%20scared.%20They%20are%20opposed%20to%20this%20plan.%20Nitish%20ji%20got%20stuck%20and%20BJP%20provided%20him%20the%20back%20door%20to%20run%20away!%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fnitish-kumar-quit-india-bloc-due-to-bihar-caste-survey-claims-rahul-gandhi-415437-2024-01-30%5C%22%3Esaid%20at%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20had%20not%20spoken%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar%20for%20the%20past%20two%20days%2C%20when%20Kumar%20suddenly%20resigned%20and%20jumped%20ship%2C%20back%20to%20the%20BJP.%20A%20little%20bit%20of%20pressure%2C%20and%20he%20makes%20a%20U-turn%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20before%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20why%20the%20pressure%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%20Because%20our%20alliance%20is%20raising%20the%20issues%20that%20matter%20to%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20started%20his%20second%20leg%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20from%20Manipur%20and%20said%20that%20Manipur%20is%20experiencing%20an%20%E2%80%9Catmosphere%20of%20civil%20war%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20yet%20to%20visit%20the%20state%20where%20ethnic%20violence%20and%20instability%20have%20continued%20since%20May%203%20last%20year%2C%20without%20any%20respite%20or%20serious%20attempts%20at%20reconciliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20President%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20was%20also%20to%20have%20been%20at%20the%20rally%20but%20inclement%20weather%20made%20it%20hard%20for%20his%20helicopter%20to%20land%20and%20Kharge%20addressed%20the%20well-attended%20public%20meeting%20by%20video%2C%20just%20before%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20spoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706624999000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F26210652%2FFufcgtmX0AQCmkG.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-bats-for-social-justice-says-nitish-kumar-exited-through-backdoor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyaya%20Yatra%20said%20INDIA%20will%20continue%20to%20raise%20social%20justice%20and%20ensure%20there%20is%20enough%20representation%20for%20groups%20without%20a%20share%20in%20power.%20He%20broke%20his%20silence%20after%20two%20days%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20defection%20to%20the%20NDA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolit