20with%20the%20logistics%2C%20while%20Harshit%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20creative%20aspect%20of%20the%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20for%20the%20family%20to%20continue%20selling%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F223780%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-harsh-kedia-diabetic-chef-guilt-free-desserts-inspiring-india-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud%20kitchen%20approach%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20Janta%20Dairy%20was%20ready%20to%20reopen.%20The%20first%20two%20years%20were%20not%20so%20much%20about%20sales%20but%20building%20a%20brand%20voice%2C%20says%20Tanay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1641993686173_11zon-1706614852.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pistabarfi%20was%20started%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20saving%20the%20family%20legacy%20from%20dying%20out%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1641993686173_11zon-1706614852.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1641993686173_11zon-1706614852-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1641993686173_11zon-1706614852-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1641993686173_11zon-1706614852-768x960.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1641993686173_11zon-1706614852-150x188.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPistabarfi%20was%20started%20to%20save%20the%20family%20legacy%20from%20dying%20out%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Harshit%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20things%20would%20set%20Pistabarfi%20apart%2C%20the%20brothers%20decided.%20The%20packaging%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20first%2C%20Harshit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20scene%20in%20India%20is%20a%20very%20unorganised%20market.%20I%E2%80%99m%20talking%20about%20the%20early%202000s%20when%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20lot%20of%20emphasis%20on%20packaging.%20Cost-cutting%20was%20rampant.%20Today%2C%20the%20scene%20has%20slightly%20improved.%20If%20you%20see%20the%20usual%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20boxes%20they%20usually%20feature%20designs%20like%20a%20cow%2C%20milk%2C%20etc.%20The%20imagery%20is%20not%20exciting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20brands%20that%20focus%20on%20good%20packaging%20do%20not%20tell%20a%20story%20through%20it.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20voice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20pain%20point%20was%20that%20of%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20tough%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Emithais%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20rival%20that%20in%20other%20cities.%20This%20is%20because%2C%20for%20quality%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20quality%20raw%20materials%20are%20needed.%20These%20are%20expensive.%20If%20employed%2C%20this%20would%20in%20turn%20increase%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20So%2C%20most%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20makers%20resort%20to%20ingredients%20that%20can%20help%20them%20achieve%20a%20balance%20between%20cost-effectiveness%20and%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPistabarfi%20is%20built%20on%20addressing%20these%20points.%20The%20brothers%20emphasise%20that%20the%20idea%20behind%20the%20venture%20has%20always%20been%20to%20stick%20to%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F248039%2Frida-sajad-noida-woman-entrepreneur-shireen-e-yemberzal-mith