ng%20caste-based%20reservations%20to%20the%20backward%20and%20marginalised%20sections%20proportional%20to%20their%20population%20in%20education%2C%20employment%20and%20welfare%20schemes%20within%20six%20months%20of%20coming%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20also%20promised%20a%20hike%20in%20reservations%20for%20BCs%20from%20the%20present%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telangana.gov.in%2Fdepartments%2Fbackward-classes-welfare%2F%5C%22%3E29%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%204%25%20reservation%20for%20Muslims%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98E%E2%80%99%20group%20of%20the%20list%20of%20BC%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fcongress-bc-declaration-promises-big-sops-for-various-communities-and-welfare-minister-for-mbcs%2Farticle67521997.ece%5C%22%3Eadopted%20a%20declaration%20at%20Kamareddy%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%2C%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20promising%20a%20hike%20in%20reservation%20for%20BCs%20in%20newly%20constituted%20local%20bodies%20from%2023%25%20to%2042%25%2C%20as%20well%20as%2042%25%20reservation%20for%20BCs%20in%20contracts%20awarded%20by%20the%20government%20in%20civil%20construction%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20annual%20budget%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%2C%20totalling%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%20in%20the%20five-year%20term%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20will%20be%20spent%20on%20the%20welfare%20of%20BCs%2C%20the%20declaration%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20134258%2FF80iGYpasAEo0kc-1024x521.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%