EAll%20the%20convicted%20persons%20filed%20appeals%20against%20their%20conviction%20and%20sentence%20before%20the%20East%20Punjab%20High%20Court%20at%20Simla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20judges%20on%20the%20special%20bench%20which%20decided%20the%20appeals%20are%20%3A-%20Justice%20A.N.%20Bhandari%2C%20Justice%20G.D.%20Khosla%20and%20Justtice%20Achhru%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E21st%C2%A0June%2C%201949%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%93%20The%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20conviction%20for%20five%20of%20the%20accused%20persons%20and%20acquitted%20two%20of%20the%20accused%20persons%20i.e.%20Dattatraya%20Parchure%20and%20Shankar%20Kistayya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAppellate%20court%20%E2%80%93%20conviction%20and%20sentence%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20551px)%2085vw%2C%20551px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30155131%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-3.51.17-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22551%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30155131%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-3.51.17-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30155131%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-3.51.17-PM-300x287.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30155131%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-3.51.17-PM-1024x978.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694926%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22527%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReasons%20for%20acquittal%20of%20Shankar%20Kisstaya%20and%20Dattatraya%20Parchure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReason%20for%20acquittal%20with%20respect%20to%20Shankar%20Kisstaya%20was%20due%20to%20insufficient%20material%20to%20justify%20the%20conviction%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReason%20for%20acquittal%20with%20respect%20of%20Dattatraya%20Parchure%20was%20that%20the%20evidence%20of%20the%20witnesses%20was%20unreliable%20and%20unsatisfactory%20and%20barring%20the%20unconfirmed%20retracted%20confession%2C%20which%20was%20actually%20involuntary%2C%20there%20is%20no%20other%20evidence%20regarding%20the%20complicity%20of%20Dattaraya%20Parchure%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20of%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20high%20court%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20noted%20that%20conspiracy%20to%20murder%20Mahatama%20Gandhi%20did%20exist.%20Apte%20and%20Nathuram%20Godse%20remained%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchief%20organisers%E2%80%9D%20throughout%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Achhru%20Ram%20and%20Justice%20Bhandari%20recommended%20the%20commutation%20of%20sentence%20of%20Gopal%20Godse%20and%20Madanlal%20Pahwa%20owing%20to%20their%20young%20age%2C%20but%20Justice%20Khosla%20disagreed%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20Justice%20Achhru%20Ram%20to%20commute%20the%20sentence%20of%20Madanlal%20Pahwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Achhru%20Ram%20observed%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20are%20quite%20young%20and%20in%20the%20bloom%20of%20their%20lives.%20Both%20seemed%20to%20have%20succumbed%20to%20influences%20exercised%20over%20them%20by%20stronger%20and%20more%20determined%20persons.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khosla%20in%20his%20one%20paragraph%20judgement%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EI%20wish%2C%20however%2C%20to%20disassociate%20myself%20from%20the%20recommendation%20for%20mercy%20made%20by%20my%20Learned%20Brother%20Achhru%20Ram%20J.%20in%20favour%20of%20Madanlal%20Pahwa.%20Pahwa%20took%20a%20very%20prominent%20part%20in%20the%20plan%20of%20conspiracy%20originally%20conceived.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bhandari%20noted%20that%20the%20observations%20of%20the%20Special%20Judge%20against%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20was%20unwarranted%20and%20that%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20impossible%20for%20any%20police%20officer%2C%20however%20capable%20and%20efficient%20he%20might%20have%20been%2C%20to%20have%20prevented%20Nathuram%20from%20committing%20the%20crime%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20question%20of%20slackness%20on%20part%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20Justice%20Bhandari%20observed%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20evidence%20on%20record%20satisfies%20me%20(a)%20that%20no%20opportunity%20was%20afforded%20to%20the%20police%20to%20explain%20the%20circumstances%20which%20prevented%20them%20from%20apprehending%20Nathuram%20before%20the%2030th%20January%20and%20thereby%20saving%20the%20life%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%3B%20(b)%20that%20Madanlal%20failed%20to%20supply%20the%20names%20of%20the%20conspirators%20to%20the%20police%3B%20(c)%20that%20even%20if%20those%20names%20were%20supplied%20it%20was%20extremely%20difficult%2C%20if%20not%20impossible%2C%20for%20the%20police%20to%20arrest%20Nathuram%20who%20was%20going%20about%20from%20place%20to%20place%20under%20assumed%20names%20and%20who%20was%20determined%20to%20assassinate%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20even%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20losing%20his%20own%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Justice%20Achhru%20Ram%3Cem%3E%C2%A0noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20concluding%201%20want%20to%20advert%20to%20some%20remarks%20made%20by%20the%20learned%20Special%20Judge%20as%20to%20the%20slackness%20shown%20in%20the%20investigation%20during%20the%20period%20between%20the%2020th%20and%20the%2030th%20January%201948%20but%20for%20which.%20in%20the%20view%20of%20the%20learned%20Judge%2C%20the%20tragedy%20could%20have%20been%20prevented.%20I%20must%20say%20that%20I%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20discover%20any%20justification%20at%20all%20for%20these%20remarks%20which%20in%20my%20judgment%20were%20wholly%20uncalled%20for.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Justice%20Khosla%3Cem%3E%C2%A0stated%20%E2%80%9CI%20concur%20with%20the%20conclusions%20arrived%20at%20by%20my%20learned%20brothers%20Bhandari%20and%20Achhru%20Ram%20JJ.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20petition%20for%20special%20leave%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20privy%20council%20was%20lodged%20by%20all%20the%20five%20who%20stood%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%20by%20the%20High%20court%20%E2%80%93%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20Apte%2C%20Karkare%2C%20Pahwa%20and%20Gopal%20Godse%20and%20the%20same%20was%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20almost%2075%20years%2C%20a%20petition%20was%20filed%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20April%202023%20alleging%20mistrial%20in%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20assassination%20case%20in%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bench%20comprising%20of%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%20and%20Justice%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20imposed%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20on%20Abhinav%20Bharat%20Congress%E2%80%99%20while%20dismissing%20the%20petition%2C%20noted%20that%2C%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20most%20misconceived%20petition%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20The%20parties%20cannot%20walk%20into%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20with%20any%20pleading%20or%20with%20any%20prayer%20they%20want.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Farticles%2Fmahatma-gandhi-murder-case-brief-facts-247956%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20LiveLaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706612453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30091446%2FIMG_1737.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fkey-facts-on-the-mahatma-gandhi-assassination-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20timeline%20of%20the%20case%20and%20details%20of%20the%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20courts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fkey-facts-on-the-mahatma-gandhi-assassination-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Freedom%20Was%20Won%2C%20Yes%2C%20But%20it%20Was%20Written%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162100%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.18%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESulekha%20Ink%20is%20the%20brand%20after%20which%20I%20was%20named%20%E2%80%98Sreelekha%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pre-independence%20Swadeshi%20ink%20conceived%20by%20my%20grandfather%20whom%20we%20fondly%20called%20Nani%20Dadu%20(Nani%20Gopal%20Maitra)%20from%20Rajshahi%20in%201934.%20The%20place%2C%20now%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20is%20where%20I%20would%20have%20been%20likely%20to%20be%20born%20if%20India%20was%20not%20partitioned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20story%20goes%20that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20Gandhiji%20%E2%80%93%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20tough%20situation%20of%20not%20having%20an%20indigenous%20ink%20to%20sign%20freedom%20petitions.%20All%20inks%20were%20manufactured%20overseas%20and%20Gandhiji%20refused%20to%20sign%20using%20any%20of%20them.%20It%20was%20at%20that%20point%20two%20brothers%20from%20Rajshahi%20took%20up%20the%20challenge.%20Nani%20Gopal%20and%20Shankacharya%20Maitra%20decided%20to%20create%20a%20homegrown%20ink%20to%20match%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20vision.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20this%20is%20the%20ink%20that%20was%20used%20to%20sign%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20in%201950.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20read%20of%20this%20creation%20story%20in%20my%20Thakuma%E2%80%99s%20(grandma%E2%80%99s)%20diaries.%20She%20was%20a%20diligent%20diary%20writer%20and%20the%20diary%20that%20I%20am%20currently%20reading%20dates%20back%20to%201952.%20Her%20writings%20cover%20incidents%20spanning%20the%20years%20around%201930%20to%201950.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20like%20entering%20a%20time%20machine.%20It%20was%20the%20thick%20of%20Swadeshi%20Movement%20that%20had%20encouraged%20the%20boycotting%20of%20foreign%20goods%20and%20the%20promotion%20of%20indigenous%20industries.%20It%20fostered%20nationalism%20in%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhiji%20had%20addressed%20his%20followers%20regarding%20the%20boycott%20of%20foreign%20goods%20in%20everyday%20life.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20went%20much%20beyond%20salt%20and%20khadi%20and%20had%20pointedly%20spoken%20about%20ink.%20But%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ell%20inks%20were%20manufactured%20overseas%20and%20Gandhiji%20refused%20to%20sign%20using%20any%20of%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162121%2FNoni-Dadu.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162121%2FNoni-Dadu.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162121%2FNoni-Dadu-300x203.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162121%2FNoni-Dadu-1024x694.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694940%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22732%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENoni%20Gopal%20Maitra%2C%20with%20others.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20Revolution%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20time%20I%20read%20Thakuma%E2%80%99s%20writings%20on%20Gandhiji%2C%20I%20pinch%20myself.%20Is%20this%20the%20Gandhiji%20of%20history%20books%3F%20Before%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhiji%20was%20arrested%20in%201932%20by%20the%20Commissionerate%20of%20Bombay%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20taken%20to%20the%20Yerawada%20Central%20Jail%20in%20Pune%2C%20he%20had%20assigned%20Satish%20Chandra%20Dasgupta%2C%20chief%20chemist%20at%20Bengal%20Chemical%2C%20with%20the%20task%20of%20creating%20a%20homegrown%20ink.%20And%20Dasgupta%20in%20turn%20had%20Nani%20Gopal%20Maitra%20in%20mind.%20Nani%20Dadu%20was%20then%20a%20physics%20teacher%20at%20Rajshahi%20University%20and%20was%20running%20an%20underground%20Swadeshi%20chapter%20of%20the%20Rajshahi%20Mukti%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajshahi%20back%20then%20was%20a%20hub%20of%20education%2C%20trade%20and%20culture%20with%20a%20major%20focus%20on%20silk%20production.%20The%20British%20invariably%20had%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20prosperous%20zones%20and%20strategically%20established%20the%20Administrative%20District%20in%201772%20and%20The%20Rajshahi%20Municipal%20Corporation%20in%201876.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThakuma%E2%80%99s%20pages%20also%20mention%20that%20Gandhiji%20used%20reed%20pens%2C%20instead%20of%20foreign-made%20fountain%20pens%20and%20that%20he%20was%20a%20prolific%20writer.%20This%20is%20entirely%20believable%2C%20since%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20letter%20collection%20itself%20runs%20into%20thousands%20of%20pages.%20Influenced%20by%20this%2C%20Thakuma%2C%20too%2C%20tried%20writing%20her%20diary%20with%20a%20reed%20pen%20which%20resulted%20in%20illegible%20handwriting%20for%20quite%20a%20few%20pages!%20Evidently%20the%20Swadeshi%20movement%20was%20raging%20through%20her%20head%20and%20heart.%20And%20this%20was%20clear%20from%20her%20mentions%20of%20what%20she%20wore%20and%20what%20she%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20diary%2C%20she%20writes%20about%20Nani%20Dadu%20being%20released%20from%20the%20jail.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAj%20khushir%20din%20%3C%2Fem%3E(today%20is%20a%20happy%20day).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162131%2Fink-pot.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162131%2Fink-pot.jpg%20669w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162131%2Fink-pot-300x226.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694941%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22505%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESulekha%20Ink%20bottles.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20behind%20bars%20for%20taking%20part%20in%20%E2%80%98Satyagraha%20Andolan%E2%80%99%20the%20non-violence%20revolution%20started%20by%20Gandhiji.%20On%20being%20released%2C%20he%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Satish%20Chandra%20Dasgupta%20(then%20chief%20chemist%20of%20Bengal%20Chemical)%20to%20meet%20Gandhiji.%C2%A0%20And%20the%20seed%20of%20a%20swadeshi%20ink%20was%20planted%20in%20his%20head.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFreshly%20designated%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20creating%20a%20homegrown%20ink%2C%20my%20grandfather%20managed%20a%20makeshift%20laboratory%20in%20the%20Maitra%20residence%20in%20Rajshahi%20and%20spent%20hours%20creating%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20ink.%20This%20ink%20was%20to%20write%20the%20freedom%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20one%20of%20my%20earliest%20memories%2C%20I%20remember%20this%20scene%20being%20enacted%20to%20me%20by%20Nani%20Dadu.%20He%20would%20mimic%20tiptoeing%20down%20the%20stairs%20and%20entering%20his%20lab.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20when%20everybody%20was%20asleep%2C%20he%20would%20unbox%20his%20secret%20formula%2C%20and%20create%20a%20magic%20potion%20called%20ink.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20Thakuma%E2%80%99s%20diary%20says%20that%20it%20was%201934%20when%20the%20black%20ink%20was%20born%20at%20the%20Maitra%20residence%20in%20Rajshahi.%20The%20family%20had%20spent%20all%20their%20jewellery%20and%20savings%20to%20make%20this%20dream%20come%20true.%20By%20July%201934%2C%20a%20box%20of%20ink%20was%20ready%20to%20leave%20for%20Gandhiji%20to%20use.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20342px)%2085vw%2C%20342px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162359%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.02.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22342%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162359%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.02.png%20894w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162359%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.02-224x300.png%20224w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162359%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.02-763x1024.png%20763w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694944%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22459%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Sulekha%20Ink%20advertisement.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhen%20a%20big%20name%20gets%20to%20name%20it%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20story%20goes%2C%20on%20August%205%2C%201934%2C%20Gandhiji%20was%20in%20Wardha%20after%20completing%20his%20Harijan%20Tour.%20Jamnalal%20Bajaj%20had%20hosted%20him%20in%20his%20house%20where%20a%20box%20of%20ink%20arrived%20at%20the%20Bajaj%20residence.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20Gandhiji%20inaugurated%20the%20ink%20by%20writing%20a%20note%20to%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20name%20it.%20And%20it%20was%20Tagore%20who%20named%20it%20Sulekha%2C%20a%20portmanteau%20for%20the%20Bengali%20phrase%20for%20%E2%80%98beautiful%20writing.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20moments%20in%20the%20diary%20are%20extraordinary.%20They%20are%20big%20as%20historical%20event%20and%20as%20a%20reader%2C%20it%20took%20me%20a%20while%20to%20let%20it%20sink%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20remember%20Thakuma%20telling%20me%20many%20times%20over%20that%20Rajshahi%20was%20synonymous%20with%20Sulekha.%20It%20is%20because%20of%20this%20that%20when%20the%20country%20was%20divided%20and%20we%20came%20to%20Calcutta%2C%20that%20a%20new%20name%20%E2%80%93%20not%20the%20same%20one%20%E2%80%93%20was%20given%20to%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20all%20of%20her%20diaries%20and%20there%20are%20indeed%20time%20lapses.%20But%20she%20does%20mention%20that%20Tagore%20dedicated%20Sulekha%20Ink%20to%20the%20nation%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20Indian%20independence.%20He%20himself%20was%20so%20charmed%20by%20the%20black%20ink%20that%20he%20used%20it%20to%20write%20some%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20literature%20of%20all%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20moment%20India%20was%20waiting%20for%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDiaries%20are%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20times.%20The%20pages%20talk%20about%20the%20legendary%20success%20of%20Sulekha%20over%20the%20decades%20and%20becoming%20a%20household%20name%20in%20Bengal.%20The%20Maitra%20brothers%20moved%20the%20ink%20manufacturing%20facility%20to%20Bowbazar%20in%20Calcutta%20in%201938.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20or%20more%20diaries%20later%2C%20I%20arrived%20at%20August%2014%2C%201947.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThakuma%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESwadhin%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eholam%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20We%20become%20independent.%20The%20bondage%20of%20colonial%20slavery%20was%20at%20last%20broken%2C%20and%20we%20were%20longer%20subjects%20of%20the%20Crown.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EForever%20etched%20in%20memory%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Nani%20Dadu%20and%20Thakuma%20have%20long%20left%20us.%20I%20moved%20to%20Bombay.%20But%20her%20diaries%20have%20found%20a%20new%20life%20with%20me.%20Who%20visited%20when%2C%20who%20stayed%20with%20us%2C%20what%20they%20ate%20that%20day%2C%20which%20doctor%20they%20went%20to%2C%20every%20detail%20was%20chalked%20down.%20But%20ever%20since%20I%20have%20been%20reading%20her%20diary%20and%20every%20time%20I%20sit%20to%20write%20on%20it%2C%20I%20tend%20to%20enter%20a%20time%20capsule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20I%20feel%20happy%20that%20she%20instilled%20the%20habit%20of%20writing%20in%20a%20diary%20in%20me.%20I%20too%20write%20regularly%2C%20if%20not%20daily.%20Always%20with%20my%20fountain%20pens%2C%20and%20this%20goes%20without%20saying%2C%20always%20with%20Sulekha%20Ink.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESreelekha%20Maitra%20is%20a%20creative%20marketing%20professional.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706611655000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162100%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.18%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fsulekha-ink-history-tagore-gandhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20homegrown%20Sulekha%20Ink%2C%20named%20by%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20and%20commissioned%20by%20Gandhi%2C%20became%20a%20sign%2C%20literally%2C%20of%20self-sufficiency%20in%20the%20days%20of%20the%20struggle%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fsulekha-ink-history-tagore-gandhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20North%20Korean%20missiles%20help%20Putin%20and%20Russia%20defeat%20Ukraine%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706610736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107261304%2Cimgsize-1226483.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A