llets%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20One%20Woman%20is%20Preserving%20Rare%20Indian%20Millets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFondly%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336185%2Fraimati-ghiuria-preserves-traditional-millets-at-her-odisha-farm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQueen%20of%20Millet%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20Raimati%20Ghiuria%2C%20a%20tribal%20farmer%20from%20Odisha%2C%20has%20preserved%2072%20traditional%20paddy%20varieties%20and%20at%20least%2030%20varieties%20of%20millets%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%3Cem%3EKundra%20bati%20mandia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20jasra%2C%20juana%2C%20and%20jamkoli%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20an%20agricultural%20family%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F257239%2Fmaharashtra-inspiring-ritwik-bhattacharya-kalote-mokashi-raigad-tribal-village-squash-professional-psa-world-tour-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20small%20tribal%20village%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Koraput%20district%2C%20a%20young%20Raimati%20was%20inspired%20by%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20Kamala%20Pujari.%20The%2070-year-old%20farmer%20taught%20Raimati%20traditional%20cultivation%20techniques%20like%20initiating%20pollination%20in%20crops%20and%20conservation%20of%20various%20kinds%20of%20native%20grains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20I%20do%20not%20remember%20any%20of%20the%20teachings%20from%20school%2C%20I%20only%20know%20how%20to%20conserve%20and%20grow%20millets%20that%20I%20learnt%20on%20the%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raimati%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20she%20was%20married%20off%20at%20the%20young%20age%20of%2016%2C%20she%20did%20not%20give%20up%20her%20dream%20of%20collecting%20and%20preserving%20millet%20varieties%20despite%20having%20to%20participate%20in%20household%20chores.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20she%20adopted%20better%20technology%20and%