%20send%20the%20suspect%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20suspect%20Nitin%20proceeded%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%2C%20but%20the%20moment%20his%20accomplice%20opened%20the%20door%20he%20sensed%20that%20something%20was%20wrong%20and%20tried%20to%20shut%20it%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20he%20was%20about%20to%20shut%20the%20door%2C%20I%20told%20one%20of%20my%20officers%20that%20we%20had%20to%20break%20these%20doors%20down.%20Luckily%2C%20there%20was%20a%20little%20gap%20on%20top%20of%20the%20iron%20grill%20door.%20One%20of%20my%20officers%20was%20able%20to%20bend%20the%20iron%20grill%20part%20of%20the%20door%20down%20and%20that%20left%20enough%20space%20for%20me%20to%20enter.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20kidnappers%20inside%20began%20firing%20at%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20As%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20a%20bullet%20hit%20Inspector%20Vinay%20Tyagi%E2%80%99s%20vest%2C%20while%20another%20hit%20commando%20Kuldip%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20this%20chaos%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20climbed%20over%20the%20bent%20iron%20grill%20and%20took%20a%20peek%20at%20the%20gap%20left%20behind%20by%20a%20second%20wooden%20door%20inside%20to%20see%20if%20the%20child%20was%20inside%20the%20main%20hall%20of%20the%20flat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20the%20boy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20there.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20ordered%20the%20personnel%20behind%20me%20to%20fire%20back.%20There%20was%20an%20exchange%20of%20fire.%20One%20of%20the%20kidnappers%20was%20shot%20down%20on%20the%20ground%20lying%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%20while%20the%20other%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20leg.%20My%20team%20immediately%20followed%20me%20inside%20while%20I%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20bedroom%20to%20find%20the%20child%20under%20a%20blanket%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuffice%20it%20to%20say%2C%20the%20child%20was%20terrified%20following%20the%20exchange%20of%20f