retaining%20the%20fragrances.%20Chemical%20fresheners%20use%20LPG%20to%20retain%20the%20fragrance.%20We%20use%20natural%20ingredients%20for%20that%20with%20no%20chemicals.%20We%20do%20not%20use%20any%20heat%2C%20water%20vapour%20or%20chemicals%20to%20diffuse%20our%20fragrances.%20We%20use%20our%20own%20Air%20Diffusion%20Technology%20with%20sensors%20to%20diffuse%20aroma%20evenly%20in%20the%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20has%20partnered%20with%20more%20than%2030%20temples%20in%20Jamshedpur%20to%20obtain%20floral%20waste.%20Every%20day%2C%20he%20collects%20a%20minimum%20of%203%20kg%20of%20floral%20waste%20from%20each%20temple.%20To%20date%2C%20he%20has%20recycled%201%2C500%20kg%20of%20temple%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20noteworthy%20aspect%20is%20that%20this%20freshener%20is%20safe%20for%20animals%20also.%20Working%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20Animal%20Welfare%20Society%20since%202018%2C%20Rajiv%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20effects%20of%20human%20behaviour%20on%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rajiv%20made%20wheelchairs%20for%20dogs%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-300x171.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-500x285.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-768x438.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-1536x876.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-