0these%20farm%20labourers%20do%20not%20have%20work%20since%20there%20are%20no%20rains%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amol%20Sainwar%2C%20founder%20and%20president%20of%20Shivprabha%20Charitable%20Trust%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336276%2Fmadhura-rajvanshi-fulbright-scholar-distinguished-award-phaltan-rural-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20situation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20grim%20for%20marginal%20farmers%20too.%20Sainwar%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20farmer%20with%20three%20acres%20of%20land%20earns%20Rs%201%2C20%2C000%20a%20year.%20But%20the%20profit%20is%20zero.%E2%80%9D%20These%20financial%20woes%20snowball%20into%20problems%20that%20affect%20each%20member%20of%20the%20household%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20standard%20of%20living.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20since%202007%2C%20Sainwar%20and%20his%20team%20have%20been%20working%20with%20underprivileged%20communities%20in%20nine%20states%20and%2043%20districts%20of%20India%20to%20bring%20equity%20in%20education%2C%20whilst%20also%20championing%20change%20in%20other%20areas%20extending%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20health%20services%2C%20electrification%2C%20rural%20development%20and%20entrepreneurship%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vision%20is%20to%20bring%20like%20minded%20people%20together%20so%20true%20change%20can%20be%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%20you%20can%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20revolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201156px)%20100vw%2C%201156px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-24-at-3.54.27-PM-1-1706162662.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20in%20remote%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%20are%20often%20unable%20to%2